Commentary: Shaheen Afridi starts with a yorker, right in the blockhole. David Warner brings his bat down in time and jams it out.
Top delivery! Good-length ball, seaming away from the southpaw, outside off. David Warner looks to defend but gets beaten on the outside edge.
This time a little wider! Length ball, outside off, shaping away. David Warner leaves it alone.
On a good length, on top of off. David Warner covers the line and respects it by blocking it down on the pitch.

David Warner gets off the mark! Length ball, shaping away a tad, on off. David Warner looks to defend but gets an outside edge. The ball rolls behind point and the batters take two. Australia get underway as well!
Touch fuller, on off. Warner blocks it off the front foot. A good over by Shaheen Afridi! 2 runs from it.
A little wayward start from Hasan Ali. Bowls a length ball down the leg side. Usman Khawaja is not troubled by that and opts to leave that alone.
Full and on the pads this time, Usman Khawaja flicks it through mid-wicket for a couple of runs. Usman Khawaja is off the mark as well!
Good-length ball, outside off, swinging away. Usman Khawaja shoulders arms to that one.
Nicely bowled! Full and angling across, outside off. Usman Khawaja is not interested in playing that.

Edged but didn't carry! Good-length ball, outside off, shaping away. Usman Khawaja looks to defend but gets an outside edge. The ball though falls well short of the second slip fielder. Usman Khawaja played it with soft hands and thus, the ball didn't get carry through.
Outside off, on a length. Usman Khawaja leaves it alone.
On a length, on middle. Warner defends it out.
Short of a length, outside off, no pace on that. David Warner was early on his shot and had to wait for the ball to come. No harm done though as he defends it out from the crease.
Slightly overpitched, on the pads. Warner prods and flicks it straight to mid-wicket.
Attacking the stumps this time, Warner presses forward and nicely defends it out.
Full again, on leg. Warner comfortably defends it out.
Shaheen Afridi is mixing his lengths well here! This time he bowls a good-length ball, outside off, shaping away. Warner offers no shot to that.
Good-length ball, on middle, at 137.3 kph. Usman Khawaja gets on top of the bounce and meets it with a dead bat.
That one stays low! Hasan Ali charges in and bowls a length ball, well outside off. Usman Khawaja lets it sail through. The ball dies on its way and Mohammad Rizwan stops it with his pads.
Short of a length, outside off. Left alone by Khawaja.
Clipped away! Full and on leg, Usman Khawaja clips it behind square on the leg side. The fielder from fine leg runs across and cuts it off. The batters settle for two.

FOUR! First boundary of the innings! A bit of a gift from Hasan Ali. Bowls it on a length, on the pads. Usman Khawaja flicks it to deep square leg. The backward square leg fielder had no chance this time to cut it off. The ball races away to the fence.
Length ball, outside off, moving away. Usman Khawaja leaves it for the keeper to collect.
Nicely bowled! Length, on off. Warner nicely nudges it on the leg side.

Half an appeal for an lbw but not given! Length ball, shaping back in, on off. David Warner is caught in the crease there. He stands up on his toes and tries to defend. Gets an inside edge onto the pads. Shaheen Afridi appeals but the umpire says no.

Big shout for lbw but once again it is not given! Shaheen Afridi is so lethal with the new ball. Good-length ball, on middle and leg, at 147 clicks. David Warner wants to stay on his back foot and tries to work it on the leg side. He is beaten by the pace and gets struck on the pads but there was an inside edge on that one as well. Pakistan doesn't opt for a review and rightly so.
An overpitched delivery this time, on off. David Warner drives it through covers and gets three runs.
On a length, on middle. Usman Khawaja stands tall and defends it back to the bowler.
Good-length ball, on off, the ball straightens up after pitching. Usman Khawaja knocks it towards covers.

Another loud appeal for LBW, but the umpire says no! A length ball, jagging back in, on the pads. David Warner once again tries to block this off the back foot, but misses and gets hit on his front pad. That was probably missing leg. That is what Mohammad Rizwan reckoned as well. Replay shows that it was indeed going down leg. Good decision by Pakistan to not go for the review.
Fraction short, outside off. David Warner taps it towards cover.

Edged..but does not that carry! Good stop though! On a length, shaping away, outside off. David Warner leans and looks to defend but gets an outside edge wide of the second slip fielder. Faheem Ashraf there dives to his left and grabs the ball on the bounce.
FOUR! Glorious! Fuller now, outside off. David Warner leans forward and drives it past cover for a beautiful boundary!
Good come back by Hasan Ali! A short ball this time, coming back in, around middle. David Warner tries to fend this away but misses and gets hit on the shoulder.
No ball! Good-length delivery, around middle. David Warner blocks it out. Hasan Ali has overstepped here and a no ball is given!
On a length, around middle and leg. David Warner nudges it towards mid-wicket.
Back of a length, shaping away, outside off. Usman Khawaja defends it out.
Tad short again, outside off. Usman Khawaja leaves it alone.
FOUR! Top shot! Shaheen Afridi overpitches this one, around off. Usman Khawaja presents the full face of the bat and drives it left of mid off for a boundary.
Full again, darting it on the pads this time. Usman Khawaja flicks it towards fine leg for a single.
On a length, shaping in, around middle. David Warner looks to drive this but ends up chipping it over the bowler's head. Two taken.
Shorter ball now, shaping in, around middle and leg. David Warner tucks it towards square leg. He calls for a single but is sent back by Usman Khawaja.
Back of a length, outside off. Usman Khawaja offers no shot to that.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Usman Khawaja pushes it towards cover. Single taken!
Nice shot! Back of a length, outside off. David Warner punches it off the back foot past point. Imam-ul-Haq cases it, slides, and keeps the ball away from the ropes. Three taken!
FOUR! Easy pickings! Not the best ball by Hasan Ali though! On a length, down the leg side. Usman Khawaja tucks it towards fine leg for a boundary!
FOUR! Back-to-back boundaries! Tad fuller now, darting it on the pads. Usman Khawaja uses his wrists and flicks it towards deep square leg for another boundary.
Once again Hasan Ali sprays it down the leg side. But this time, Usman Khawaja decides to leave it untouched.
On a length, outside off. David Warner pushes it towards the cover-point region.
Fuller now, wide of off. David Warner leans to drive, but he drags it with the inner half of his bat towards mid off.
Tad full again, around off. David Warner taps it towards cover.
FOUR! Beautiful shot! Shaheen Afridi serves another fuller delivery, outside off. David Warner presses forward and drives it uppishly over cover for a boundary!
Good change of length by Shaheen Afridi! A short ball now, around middle. David Warner does well to lean back and let that go through to the keeper.
Back of a length, outside off, at around 140 clicks. David Warner defends it out.
Faheem Ashraf begins with a full ball, outside off. Usman Khawaja blocks it out off the front foot.
Full once again, outside off. Usman Khawaja pushes it towards cover.
Good ball by Faheem Ashraf! Back of a length, shaping away a tad, at 131.6 clicks. Usman Khawaja stays in his crease and looks to defend this, but gets an outside edge away from gully.
Fraction short again, around middle. Usman Khawaja blocks this one.
FOUR! Lovely shot! Another short ball, on middle. Usman Khawaja picks up the length, and pulls it towards deep square leg for a boundary.
On a length, around off. Usman Khawaja shows the full face of his bat and defends it out.
Full and drifting it on leg, David Warner pushes it back to the bowler.
Floats it up, outside off. David Warner defends it to the off side.
Short and on leg, David Warner moves leg side and punches it towards covers.
Tosses it up nicely, on off. David Warner gets on the back foot and blocks it out.

SIX! Intent from David Warner! Tossed up, outside off. David Warner shimmies down and tonks it over long off. Didn't hit it from the middle of the bat but still have enough legs to go the distance. A maximum!
Slower through the air, outside off. David Warner hangs back and cuts it to point.
Fuller, on middle. Usman Khawaja eases it to mid off.
Around off, on a length. Usman Khawaja looks to defend with soft hands. The ball goes off the outside edge to gully.
Length ball, outside off, shaping away. Usman Khawaja shoulders arms to that one.
Good-length ball, outside off. Usman Khawaja lets it sail through.
Length ball, on leg. Usman Khawaja works it through mid-wicket and rotates the strike.
FOUR! Good shot! Short of a length, on middle, at 129 clicks. David Warner rides the bounce and gets himself into a good posiition. Pulls it nicely and over mid-wicket to bag another boundary.
Loopy ball, on off, Usman Khawaja goes back and pats it back to the bowler.

Brilliant bowling from Sajid Khan! Usman Khawaja can count himself lucky there. Sajid Khan tosses it up, around off, turning away. Usman Khawaja charges down and looks to go for the big shot. The ball goes off the outside edge over the slip fielder to third man for a brace.
Flighted delivery, on leg. Blocked out.
Tosses it up, on off. Usman Khawaja drives it to mid off for a single.
Outside off, cut away but straight to point.
Floats it up, on middle. Warner blocks it off the back foot.
Length ball, attacking the stumps. Usman Khawaja lunges forward and defends it out.
Outside off, on a length. Usman Khawaja lets it sail through.
Fuller, on off. Usman Khawaja leans and drives it back. Faheem Ashraf does well to get low and stop it on his followthrough.
FOUR! Lovely shot! A juicy half-tracker, on middle and leg. Usman Khawaja swivel-pulls it well and to deep mid-wicket. That was hit with some power and it races away to the ropes in a flash.
Touch fuller, on off. Usman Khawaja pushes it firmly towards cover.
On a good length, on off. Usman Khawaja watchfully defends it towards covers again.
Floats it up, outside off. David Warner hangs back and cuts it to deep cover for a single.
Loopy ball, around off. Usman Khawaja stays back and taps it to the off side.
Tosses it up, on off. Nice flight on that one as well. Usman Khawaja prods and blocks it out.
Usman Khawaja comes down the track and takes it on full. Flicks it straight to mid-wicket.
Flighted delivery, on off. Usman Khawaja stays solid in his defence.
Tosses it up, on middle. Usman Khawaja uses his feet and works it to mid on. Keeps the strike with the single.
On a length, shaping back in on middle. Usman Khawaja blocks it out solidly.
Touch fuller, around off, at 137 clicks. Usman Khawaja pushes it back to the bowler.
Outside off, on a fuller length, at 134.2 clicks. Usman Khawaja leans and taps it cover-point.
Faheem Ashraf pulls his length ball a tad, outside off. Usman Khawaja leaves it alone.
Fraction shorter now, around off. Usman Khawaja defends it towards point.
On a length, around off. Usman Khawaja presses forward and blocks it out. A maiden!
Tosses it up, on a fuller length, on middle. David Warner defends it with the inner half of his bat.
Loopy once again, fuller in length, around off. David Warner leans and defends it out.
Tad quicker, on the pads, full again. David Warner tucks it towards fine leg for a single.
SIX! Up and over! Loopy ball, turning away a tad, around off, full in length. Usman Khawaja shimmies down the ground and tonks it over long off for a biggie.
Tosses it up again, around off. Usman Khawaja pushes it uppishly wide of the bowler, who dives to his right but fails to reach the ball. Single taken!

SIX! This time David Warner goes big! Both the batters have decided to take on the spinner. Another full ball, around middle. David Warner dances down the track and smashes it straight down the ground for another maximum of the over! 14 runs off the over!
Angling in, around middle, on a length. Usman Khawaja defends it out.
Fuller now, around off. Usman Khawaja whips it towards mid on. Shaheen Afridi slides and fails to stop the ball. A sloppy effort by him, allows the batters to take two runs!
Angling in again, on a length, around off. Usman Khawaja blocks it out.
Tad slower now, on a length, around middle and leg. Usman Khawaja pushes it past mid-wicket for a single.
On a length, outside off. David Warner leans and defends it out.

OUT! CAUGHT BEHIND! Faheem Ashraf strikes and draws first blood! A much-needed wicket for Pakistan, they get rid of the dangerous David Warner! A peach of a delivery by Faheem Ashraf. On a length, shaping away, outside off. David Warner stays in his crease and looks to block this, but he gets an outside edge towards the keeper. Mohammad Rizwan pouches it safely. Delight for Pakistan! Faheem Ashraf is finally rewarded for bowling consistently and keeping it tight.
Howout: c Mohammad Rizwan b Faheem Ashraf

Commentary: Nauman Ali begins with a loopy ball, full, around off. Usman Khawaja defends it out.
FOUR BYES! Fuller, down the leg side this time. Usman Khawaja misses his flick, Mohammad Rizwan fails too to grab the ball and it races away to the fine leg fence for a boundary.
Tosses it up, very full, around middle. Usman Khawaja works it away towards mid on for a single.
Slower through the air, full, on middle. Marnus Labuschagne lunges and defends it out.
Flighted delivery, pitches it up again, around off. Marnus Labuschagne drives it to the fielder at mid off.
Tad quicker now! Fuller ball, at 90.4 clicks, on middle. Marnus Labuschagne shows the full face of his bat and defends it out.
Fuller ball, around off. Usman Khawaja defends it towards mid off.
Faheem Ashraf pitches it up again, outside off. Usman Khawaja leans and blocks it out.
On a length, outside off. Usman Khawaja drives it to the fielder at cover.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Usman Khawaja defends it out.

FOUR! Streaky! Length ball, outside off. Usman Khawaja leans to block this, but the ball goes off the outside edge past gully for a boundary. That will be 50 for Usman Khawaja! It's been a good innings so far, he has looked in good touch. His second fifty of the series.
Fuller ball, outside off. Usman Khawaja defends it towards cover.
Loopy ball, on middle. Marnus Labuschagne presses forward and blocks it out.
Floats it up, on off. Marnus Labuschagne is watchful in his defence.
Quicker, on middle. Played to short leg.
Full and on middle, pushed back to the bowler.
Slightly short, around off. Marnus Labuschagne works it on the leg side.

OUT! RUN OUT! Needless from Australia and Pakistan will be on cloud 9 seeing the back of Marnus Labuschagne. Nauman Ali bowls a flatter delivery, on middle. Marnus Labuschagne leans and drives it to mid off. He sets off for a quick single. Sajid Khan has three stumps to aim at and he does so by collecting it with his right hand quickly and hitting the bullseye. Pakistan are already celebrating but the umpire takes it upstairs to confirm. Replay shows that Marnus Labuschagne is caught short of his crease. He walks back with disappointment on his face. He goes for 0 and what a big moment in the game.
Howout: run out (Sajid Khan)

Commentary: Fuller ball, around middle and off. Steven Smith defends it out.
Angling in on middle, on a length. Steven Smith blocks it out.
Shaping back in again, on middle, good-length delivery. Steven Smith walks across and defends it out.
Fuller in length, on off. Steven Smith moves across and nudges it to mid-wicket.
Length ball, on off. Smith covers the line and blocks it out.
First maiden for Hasan Ali! On a length, on off. Smith defends it out moving across.
Full and wide, outside off. Usman Khawaja pushes it to point for a single.
Full and on off, driven towards covers.
Tosses it up, outside off. Steven Smith charges down and defends it uppishly back to the bowler.
On off, Smith defends it solidly off the front foot.
Loopy ball, outside off. Smith leans and blocks it to the off side.
Outside off, Smith fends it to point off the outer half of the bat and gets a single. He is off the mark and will keep the strike as well.
Good-length ball, on off. Smith blocks it off the back foot towards mid on.
Short of a length, on leg. Smith moves across and tucks it behind square on the leg side for a single.
Good-length ball, on off. Usman Khawaja defends it back to the bowler.
Fuller, on off. Usman Khawaja taps it to point.
Usman Khawaja clips this length ball to mid-wicket.
Outside off, on a length. Usman Khawaja leaves it alone.
FOUR! Steven Smith showing some intent now. Gets to the pitch of the ball by advancing down the track and lofts it over the bowler's head for a boundary.
Flatter delivery, on off. Steven Smith punches it towards covers.
Full and on off, Steven Smith drives it straight to cover.
Loopy ball, on middle. Smith knocks it back to the bowler.
Flatter delivery, outside off. Steven Smith punches it towards cover.
Flatter once again, on off. Smith stays solid in his defence.
Good-length ball, outside off, angling across. Usman Khawaja lets it sail though.
Back of a length, on middle. Usman Khawaja gets on the back foot and defends it out.
Touch fuller on this occasion, on off. Usman Khawaja stays solid in his defence.
Full, on middle. Usman Khawaja moves across and blocks it out.
On a good length, on off. Usman Khawaja knocks it back to the bowler.
Very full, on middle. Driven to mid on.
Flighted delivery, on off. Steven Smith prods and drives it to long off for a single.
Loopy, full and on off. Pushed back to the bowler.
Full, outside off. Usman Khawaja pushes it towards covers for a single.
Tossed up, on off. Steven Smith presses forward and defends it to the off side.
Flatter ball, outside off. Steven Smith watches it closely and shoulders arms.
Full and on off, Steven Smith presses forward and blocks it out. THAT WILL BE LUNCH ON DAY 1!
Shaheen Afridi starts with a full ball, on off. Usman Khawaja prods and flicks it to mid-wicket.
Fuller in length, on off. Usman Khawaja drives it to mid off.
Full again, outside off. Usman Khawaja drives it towards cover this time.
First runs in this session! Length ball, on middle and leg. Usman Khawaja eases it to deep mid-wicket. Calls for two and gets it easily.
Good-length ball, on off. Usman Khawaja gets behind the line and meets it with a dead bat.
Length ball, angling in, outside off. Usman Khawaja defends it to the off side.
Loopy ball, turning away, on off. Steven Smith pushes it back to the bowler off the back foot.
Flatter ball, angling in with the arm, on leg. Steven Smith steps out and defends it to mid on.
Magnificent delivery! Tosses it up, outside off, turning away. Steven Smith presses forward to defend but gets beaten on the outside edge.
On off, blocked out.
Flatter, on the pads. Steven Smith tucks it to deep square leg for a couple of runs.
Full, on off. Smith lunges forward to block.
Short ball to begin the over, on middle. Usman Khawaja ducks underneath.
On a good length, around off. Usman Khawaja stands tall and watchfully defends.

NO BALL AND FOUR! That's a glorious stroke! Nice and full, on the pads. Usman Khawaja uses the pace of the bowler and flicks it nicely to deep mid-wicket. Puts his wrists to good use and gets a boundary. Shaheen Afridi has overstepped here and will have to reload.
Fuller in length, on middle. Usman Khawaja drives it back to the bowler. Shaheen Afridi collects the ball and mimes a throw at him.
Goes full again, on middle. Usman Khawaja again drives it back to the bowler. A slight stare from Shaheen Afridi but Usman Khawaja puts a cheeky smile.
Shaheen Afridi is trying too hard here. Bangs a bouncer down leg. Usman Khawaja sits under it. Mohammad Rizwan does well to move to his right and collect the ball.
Another bouncer to end the over! Usman Khawaja ducks again. Stare again from Shaheen Afridi! Looks like he is frustrated after conceding that boundary.
Loopy ball, outside off, fuller ball. Steven Smith leans and defends it out.
FOUR! Good aggression by Steven Smith! Another fuller ball, tad slower through the air, on middle. Steven Smith shimmies down the track and smashes it down the ground for a cracking boundary.
Tosses it up, full, around off. Steven Smith presses forward and defends it out.
Touch quicker now, on the pads, fullish ball. Steven Smith flicks it past mid-wicket. Two taken!
Slower through the air, on middle. Steven Smith shows the full face of his bat and blocks it out solidly.
Very full, loopy ball, outside off. Steven Smith knocks it down to long off for a single. He retains the strike!
Good-length delivery, around off, at 137.1 clicks. Steven Smith walks across and tucks it towards square leg for a single.

Half an appeal for LBW, but the umpire is unmoved! Another length delivery, angling in, on the pads. Usman Khawaja looks to flick this but misses and gets rapped on his front pad. That looked like it was sliding down leg!
Shaping away, on a length, outside off. Usman Khawaja opens the face of his bat and taps it towards point.
Angling in on the pads, tad fuller. Usman Khawaja flicks it gently past mid-wicket for a single.
Shaheen Afridi goes 'round the wicket to the right-hander, serves a length ball, shaping back in around middle. Steven Smith walks across and tucks it to the fielder at square leg.
Tad fuller, darting it on the pads. Steven Smith taps it towards mid-wicket and scampers through to the other end. Steven Smith will keep strike for the next over!
Flighted delivery, full in length, around off. Steven Smith has defended it out.
Fuller again, loopy ball, around middle. Steven Smith blocks it out watchfully.
Floats it up, around middle, pitches it up. Steven Smith lunges and defends it out.
Slower through the air, very full, around off. Steven Smith eases it down to long off for a single.
Tad shorter now, turning it in on middle. Usman Khawaja stays in his crease and works it towards mid-wicket.
Loopy ball, on middle, fuller ball. Usman Khawaja steps down the pitch and pushes it back towards the bowler.
FOUR! Nicely done! Shaheen Afridi drops it short, around off. Steven Smith stays back, waits for it, and dabs it past gully for a boundary.
Another shorter ball, around middle. Steven Smith pulls it towards the fielder at square leg.
Back of a length, around middle. Steven Smith pulls it gently past square leg and rotates the strike.
Shaheen Afridi bowls a short ball again, down the leg side. Usman Khawaja leaves it alone. Mohammad Rizwan fails to grab the ball and gets hit on his pads.
On a length, around middle and leg. Usman Khawaja nudges it towards mid-wicket.
Back of a length, down the leg side. Usman Khawaja pulls it towards deep square leg for a single.
Tad quicker, on middle. Usman Khawaja stays in his crease and defends this one out.
This one lands on a fuller length, slower through the air, on middle. Usman Khawaja presses forward and blocks it out watchfully.
Another loopy ball, full again, around middle. Usman Khawaja knocks it down to long on. Single taken!
Quicker, around middle. Steven Smith pushes it towards cover off the back foot.
Tossed up delivery, around off. Steven Smith has blocked this off the front foot.
Another loopy ball, full in length, on middle. Steven Smith lunges and defends it out.
Drifting on the pads, Usman Khawaja stays back and blocks it out.
Tossed up, full and on middle. Usman Khawaja pushes it back to the bowler.
Short and on off, Usman Khawaja rocks back and punches it towards covers for a run.
Floats it up, on leg. Steven Smith tucks it to deep square leg for one.
On middle, punched to long off this time by Usman Khawaja. He takes a single.
Loopy ball, on middle. Steven Smith works it on the leg side for another single.
Flatter, on middle, the ball stays a touch low as well. Steven Smith does well to block it out.
Tossed up, around off. Steven Smith watches it closely and defends it to the off side.
Given some loop, full and on off. Smith defends it back to the bowler.
Slower through the air, on off. Smith drives it through cover-point and crosses ends.
Sharp turn! Loopy ball, coming in from outside off. Usman Khawaja is taken aback by the turn. Does well in the end to defend it to mid-wicket.
This is worked to mid on for a single.
FOUR! Usman Khawaja is so good at picking up the length. This was a tad short, on the pads and Usman Khawaja pulls it nicely to deep square leg for a boundary.
On the pads again, Usman Khawaja glances it down to fine leg for a brace.
Full and on leg, clipped on the leg side.
Quicker delivery, outside off. Usman Khawaja stays back and cuts it but finds the point fielder.
Full and outside off, Usman Khawaja blocks it out.

FOUR! A boundary to start and a boundary to end the over! Flatter delivery, going down leg. Usman Khawaja sweeps it along the carpet towards the fine leg region. The fielder there misfields as he allows the ball to go through. A boundary! That brings up the 50-run stand between these two!
Full and on off, Steven Smith drives it to the left of the bowler. Nauman Ali dives that side and stops the ball tumbling over.
Full again, driven back to the bowler again.
Loopy ball, on middle. Pushed nicely to long off for a single.
FOUR! Nicely timed! Tossed up, outside off. Usman Khawaja gets low and sweeps it to deep square leg. Sublime timing on that one and he gets another boundary.
Full and outside off, Usman Khawaja drills it down to long on for one.
On the pads, clipped to short fine leg for a single. 150 up for Australia!
Fuller in length, outside off. Steven Smith pushes it to the off side.
Length ball, tailing back in to the right-hander, on off. Steven Smith covers the line and defends it to mid on.
Length ball, outside off. Smith with a watchful leave this time.
On a good length, on middle. Smith defends it watchfully moving across.
Fuller in length, outside off. Steven Smith knocks it in front of the mid off fielder.
An overpitched delivery, on the pads. Steven Smith flicks it behind square on the leg side for a couple of runs.
Loopy ball, full, around off. Usman Khawaja eases it down to long off and rotates the strike.
Slower through the air, around middle. Steven Smith pushes it towards long on for a single.
Floats it up, full, around off. Usman Khawaja presses forward and drives it to long off for a single.
Slower through the air, around off, fuller ball, at 80.5 clicks. Steven Smith lunges and blocks it out.
Fuller again, turning it in on middle. Steven Smith stays in his crease and tucks it towards square leg for a single.
Much slower again, loopy ball, pitches it up, on middle. Usman Khawaja blocks it out.
Very full, around middle and leg. Steven Smith taps it to mid-wicket.
Back of a length, outside off. Steven Smith stays back and tries to cut this away, but gets a bottom edge back onto the deck.

Leg bye! A length ball, around the pads, at 133.3 clicks. Steven Smith looks to tuck this away, but he misses and the ball deflects off his pads and goes towards fine leg. The batters steal a leg bye!
Length ball, angling in, around the pads. Usman Khawaja defends it towards the left of the bowler.
Outside off, on a length. Usman Khawaja blocks it out off the back foot.
Angling in, around middle and leg. Usman Khawaja defends it with the outer half of his bat towards cover.
On a length ball, tailing back in on middle. Steven Smith defends it out.
Back of a length, angling down the leg side. Steven Smith looks to tuck this away but bails out at the end.
Good-length delivery, outside off, shaping away. Steven Smith taps it towards point.
Angling in on the pads, on a length, at 136 clicks. Steven Smith works it away towards deep square leg and rotates the strike.
Fuller ball, outside off. Usman Khawaja drives but finds the fielder at mid off.
On a length, around off. Usman Khawaja defends it out.
Fuller ball, around middle. Steven Smith pushes it uppishly towards square leg for a single.
Fuller ball, outside off. Usman Khawaja taps it towards point and rotates the strike.
Angling in, around middle, tad fuller. Steven Smith taps it towards the fielder at short mid-wicket.
Another fuller ball, on the pads. Steven Smith defends it out towards mid-wicket.
Full toss now, around middle and leg. Steven Smith tucks it toward mid-wicket. No run there!
Very full, on middle. Steven Smith blocks it out towards square leg.
Swing and a miss! Shorter and wide of off. Usman Khawaja stays in his crease and looks to chop this away but misses.
Back of a length, shaping away, outside off. Usman Khawaja taps it towards gully. No run there!
Fraction shorter, on middle. Usman Khawaja hangs back and defends it out.

Bye! Beaten! A beauty by Faheem Ashraf! On a length, shaping away just a tad, around the fifth stump line. Usman Khawaja looks to defend this but misses and gets beaten on the outside edge. Mohammad Rizwan fails to grab the ball and the ball rolls just past the keeper's helmet which is placed on the ground behind him. One taken! It would have been 5 runs had it hit the helmet there!
Fuller, on the pads. Steven Smith shuffles across and tucks it away towards fine leg for a single.
Another jaffa! On a length, outside off, shaping away. Usman Khawaja looks to block this off the back boot, but he misses and the ball zips past the outside edge.
On a good length, outside off, shaping away. Steven Smith offers no shot to that.
Back of a length, on off. Steven Smith stands tall and fends it to the off side.
A bit of width offered! Back of a length, outside off. Steven Smith works it to cover.
Keeps it full this time, on off. Driven straight to mid off.
Length ball, angling in, on middle. Steven Smith moves across and defends it to mid on.
Fuller, outside off. Steven Smith drives it well but could not find the gap. Driven to the cover-point fielder.
Length ball, well outside off. Usman Khawaja goes chasing after it and the ball goes off the toe end of the bat towards the slip cordon.
Back of a length, on off. Usman Khawaja blocks it from the crease.
Good-length ball, outside off. This time Usman Khawaja doesn't go chasing. Left if for the keeper to collect.
On a length, outside off. Usman Khawaja is not interested in playing that.
Touch fuller, on off. Usman Khawaja drives it to mid off.
Length, outside off. Usman Khawaja is not tempted by that. He shoulders arms and lets that one go.
On a good length, shaping away a bit, outside off. Steven Smith lets it be.
Length ball, outside off. Steven Smith leaves it alone. The ball dies on it's way and doesn't carry to Mohammad Rizwan.
Full and outside off, Steven Smith defends it out.
A low full toss, on off. Steven Smith keeps it out. Maybe, Shaheen Afridi is searching for that inswinging yorker.
Good-length ball, outside off, Steven Smith leaves it untouched.
Full and on off, Steven Smith dabs it awkwardly towards gully. Three maidens in a row for Pakistan!
On a length, outside off. Usman Khawaja defends it to the off side.
Outside off, on a length. Usman Khawaja shoulders arms.
On a length, outside off. Usman Khawaja lets it sail through.
First runs after 21 dots! Fuller and on the pads, Usman Khawaja flicks it to deep square leg for a brace.

Fuller in length, on off. Usman Khawaja covers the line and drives it to mid on. Hasan Ali slides to his right and stops the ball. After that, shows his dance steps for the fans. He's quite a character!
On off, blocked out.
Length ball, outside off. Steven Smith choses not to play.
Length ball, angling across, outside off. Steven Smith moves across and leaves it alone.
Fuller ball, angling in around the pads. Steven Smith flicks it towards square leg.
On a length, around middle and off. Steven Smith shuffles across and defends it towards mid-wicket.
An inswinging yorker, on leg. Steven Smith does well to jam it out.
Goes for the yorker again but ends up bowling a low full toss, on off. Steven Smith blocks it out.
Loopy ball, full, on middle. Usman Khawaja defends it out.
Tad shorter, turning it in, around middle. Usman Khawaja shuffles across and taps it towards square leg for a single.
Nauman Ali goes 'round the wicket, serves a fuller ball, turning it away, outside off. Steven Smith leans and leaves it alone.
Tosses it up, full, around off. Steven Smith drives and finds the fielder at cover.
Outside, turning away, fuller ball. Steven Smith blocks it out.
Quicker, around off, fuller in length. Steven Smith stays back and defends it out.
Very full ball, swinging it in, around off. Usman Khawaja pushes it towards cover.
Another full ball, swinging it in late, around middle. Usman Khawaja closes the face of his bat and drives it towards mid on.
On a length, outside off, shaping away a tad. Usman Khawaja hangs back and taps it towards point.
Shaheen Afridi pitches it up again, outside off. Usman Khawaja opens the face of his bat and guides it towards point.
Shaheen Afridi pulls his length back now, tailing back in on middle. Usman Khawaja blocks it out.
Shaheen Afridi drops it short now, around middle. Usman Khawaja ducks underneath it. Shaheen Afridi walks and stares at Usman Khawaja with a cheeky smile! A maiden over!
Loopy ball, full, around middle. Steven Smith leans and defends it out.
Another fuller ball, around middle. Steven Smith presses forward and blocks it out.
Quicker this time, around middle, fuller ball. Steven Smith hangs back and blocks it out.
Quicker again, coming in with the angle this one, around middle. Steven Smith looks to defend this, but the ball goes off the inside edge on the leg side.
FOUR! Lovely shot! Very full, slower through the air, on middle. Steven Smith waits for it and whips it past mid on for a boundary. He moves to 40 with that!
Flatter ball, now, on middle. Steven Smith defends it out off the back foot.
TWO LEG BYES! Quicker ball, darting it on the pads. Usman Khawaja misses his flick and the ball brushes off his pads and goes towards fine leg. Two taken!
Flatter ball, quick again, around middle. Usman Khawaja blocks it out off the back foot.
Tad shorter, around middle. Usman Khawaja blocks it towards cover.
Short again, spinning away, outside off. Usman Khawaja pushes it off the back foot towards cover for a single.
Turning it in to the right-hander, fuller ball, on middle. Steven Smith defends it out.
Touch shorter, around off. Steven Smith blocks it out. That will be Tea on Day 1!
Tosses it up, full, outside off. Usman Khawaja leans and blocks it out.

In the air...but safe! Outside off, fuller ball, turning it in. Usman Khawaja shuffles across and looks to push this away, but gets an outside edge, onto the keeper's knee. The ball lobs up over the slip fielder and the batters sneak in a run.
FOUR! Top shot! Shorter ball, wide of off. Steven Smith hangs back and slashes it past cover for a cracking boundary.
Much straighter now, tosses it up around off. Steven Smith defends it out.
Very full, around middle, loopy ball. Steven Smith leans and blocks it out.
Turning it around middle. Steven Smith shuffles across and taps it towards square leg. 5 runs off the first over after Tea!
Full and sliding down leg, Usman Khawaja flicks it to square leg.
Flighted delivery, on off. Usman Khawaja presses forward to block.
Loopy ball, full and outside off. Usman Khawaja drives it towards coves.
Tossed up, outside off. Usman Khawaja pushes it to long off for a run.
On leg, tucked to square leg.
Full and outside off. Steven Smith opens the bat-face and drives it past Shaheen Afridi at mid off for a couple of runs.
Full and well outside off. Usman Khawaja reaches out for it and sweeps it to deep mid-wicket for a single.
Flighted delivery, on off. Smith drives it towards covers.
Flatter, on off. Smith hangs back and meets it with a dead bat.
Full, on off. Smith prods and eases it down to mid on for a run.
Tossed up, around the fourth stump line. Usman Khawaja keeps it out.
A single to end the over! Given a bit of air, outside off. Usman Khawaja taps it to the off side gently and crosses ends.
Fuller, on middle. Usman Khawaja clips it to mid-wicket.
Full again, on middle. Driven back to the bowler.

Cries of catch it but the ball lands safe! Loopy ball, on leg. Usman Khawaja tries to work it on the leg side. Gets a leading edge and the ball falls well short of the cover fielder. He is in the 90s and would not like to depart before scoring his ton.
Around off, blocked out.
On the pads, Usman Khawaja tickles it down to fine leg. Calls for two and gets it comfortably. Good running!
Tossed up, on middle. Kept out by Usman Khawaja.
Outside off, Steven Smith is not bothered to play any shot to that and leaves it alone.
Full and on middle, Steven Smith prods and nudges it to wide of mid on. Shaheen Afridi there does well to dive to his right and stop the ball. Keeps it down to a single.
Fuller, outside off. Pushed to extra cover.
FOUR! Usman Khawaja picks this superbly! Wonderful stroke! Full and on middle, Usman Khawaja gets low on his knee and sweeps it to deep square leg for a boundary. He moves to 96!
On off, turning in. Usman Khawaja stays back and defends it watchfully.
Tossed up, on off. Usman Khawaja is very solid in his defence.
Loopy ball, on middle. Smith works it on the leg side.
Smith uses his feet and gets to the pitch of the ball. Eases it down to mid on for a single. He moves to 49! 100-run stand between these two!
This is pushed back to the bowler.
Short and on off, punched towards covers off the back foot.
Flatter and quicker, on middle. Usman Khawaja guides it back to the bowler.
Usman Khawaja works this through square and keeps the strike. He moves to 97!
Fuller ball, turning it in, around middle. Usman Khawaja shuffles across and tucks it towards short leg.
Loopy ball, full again, outside off. Usman Khawaja leans and defends it out.
Tad quicker now, outside off, full in length. Usman Khawaja hops back in his crease and blocks it out.
Tosses it up, outside off. Usman Khawaja presses forward and drives it to the fielder at cover.
Flighted delivery, fuller ball, outside off. Usman Khawaja has leff that alone.
Very full again, around off. Usman Khawaja defends it out. A maiden over!
Full, darting it on the pads. Steven Smith tucks it towards square leg.
Loopy ball, flatter, around middle and leg. Steven Smith works it away towards square leg.
Full, around off. Steven Smith defends it out.
Very full, on middle. Steven Smith pushes it towards mid on.
Loopy ball, full, outside off. Steven Smith leans and blocks it out.
Fuller ball, around middle and leg. Steven Smith clips it towards square leg for a single. 50 for Steven Smith! A solid innings by him so far, he will want to carry on and make a big score from here!
Tosses it up, outside off. Steven Smith leaves it alone.
Shorter ball, down the leg side. Steven Smith brings his pads in the way.
Another shorter ball, once again down the leg side. Steven Smith once again, lets it go off his pads.
Fuller ball, down the leg side. Steven Smith leans and pads it away.
Slower through the air, fuller ball, around middle. Steven Smith knocks it down to long off for a single.
Shorter ball, wide of off. Usman Khawaja pushes it off the back foot towards deep cover for a single. He moves to 98 and he will retain the strike.
Shorter ball, outside off. Usman Khawaja stays in his crease and cuts it towards point. No run there!
Fuller ball, firing it on the pads. Usman Khawaja flicks it towards square leg for a single. He moves to 99 with that!
Leg bye! Angling it down the leg side, shorter ball. Steven Smith misses his tuck and the ball brushes off his pads towards fine leg. Leg bye taken!
Fuller ball, on middle. Usman Khawaja leans and defends it out.

There it is! 100 for Usman Khawaja! A fuller ball, on the pads. Usman Khawaja leans and taps it towards square leg for a single. He missed out on his century in the first Test, but he made sure he got it this time! What an innings it has been so far! That is his 11th Test hundred. He raises his bat and acknowledges the ovation! Steven Smith walks to him and hugs the southpaw. Usman Khawaja is the fourth Australian to score a hundred at the National Stadium! Australia's first of the tour and it has been as good an innings as it can get.
Full and on middle, Steven Smith keeps it out.
Slower through the air, wide of off. Usman Khawaja taps it towards point and rotates the strike.
Fuller ball, around middle and leg. Steven Smith leans and defends it out.
Full again, down the leg side. Steven Smith keeps it away with his pads.
Nauman Ali pulls his length back now, down the leg side again. Steven Smith leaves it alone.
Loopy ball, full in length, down leg. Steven Smith leans and pads it away.
Tosses it up, full, around middle this time. Steven Smith presses forward and defends it out.
Pakistani spinners are constantly trying to bowl it in the rough. Another ball, down leg. Usman Khawaja pads it away.
Once again it is bowled down the leg side. Usman Khawaja brings his pads into play.
WIDE! This is way down the leg side. Usman Khawaja leaves it alone and the umpire gives it as a wide.
Yet another ball, on the pads. Usman Khawaja doesn't bother playing that one.
On the pads and it has kicked that away.
Full and on middle, pushed back to the bowler.
Negative line once again by Sajid Khan, loopy ball down leg. Usman Khawaja gets struck on the pads and the ball rolls to short fine leg.
Tossed up, tunring in from outside leg. Steven Smith pads it away. The ball lobs up and the first slip fielder takes it.
Full and on leg, padded away.
Flighted delivery, on middle. Smith pushes it towards covers.
Loopy ball, on off. Steven Smith tries to work it on the leg side but gets an inside edge onto the pads.
WIDE! Full and down the leg side. Smith offers no shot. Wided.
Full and on leg, Smith moves leg side and eases it to long on for a single.
Floats it up, on off, extra bounce on that as well. Usman Khawaja fends it to the leg side one-handed. He looks for a single but is sent back.
Flatter ball down the leg side. Steven Smith works it to deep square leg for a single.
Full and on leg, Usman Khawaja presses forward and pads it away.
Way down the leg side. Usman Khawaja leaves it untouched.
Full and on the pads, Usman Khawaja is happy to keep it out with his pads.
On middle, blocked out.
Full and on middle, Usman Khawaja pushes it to long off for a single.
Tossed up delivery around middle and leg, Khawaja drives it to long on for a single.
Tossed up, on leg. Steven Smith pads it away.
Full and on middle, Steven Smith is solid in his defence.
Nauman Ali continuing with these negative lines. Bowls it down the leg side. Steven Smith hangs back and pads it away.
Ali keeps bowling down leg and Smith keeps kicking them away. Every ball looks like a deja vu for the moment.
Flighted ball, on middle. Steven Smith defends it out.
Full and on leg, Usman Khawaja plays it to mid-wicket.
WIDE! Down the leg side and this time it has been given as a wide.
Shortish, on middle. Usman Khawaja punches it towards mid on.
Drifting on the pads, Usman Khawaja works it to through mid-wicket for a single.
On the pads again and Smith nudges it through mid-wicket for a run.
Floated delivery, on leg. Usman Khawaja kicks it away.
Loopy ball down the leg side, Usman Khawaja looks to clip but misses. The ball goes off his pads to short fine leg.
Fuller ball, down the leg side. Steven Smith leans and pads it away.
Full again, down the leg side. Steven Smith pushes it behind the keeper, towards short fine leg.
Loopy ball, down leg once again. Steven Smith keeps it away with his pads.

Shorter ball, coming on middle. Steven Smith covers the stumps and lets the ball hit him on the pads. A stifled appeal there for LBW, but the umpire is unmoved. The ball was pitching outside leg. Nauman Ali wanted to review this one, but all the Pakistan players deny it. Steven Smith shares a laugh as well!
Shorter ball, down the leg side. Steven Smith keeps it away with his pads.
Tosses it up up, around middle and leg. Steven Smith once again covers the stumps and lets the ball hit him on his pads.
Wide! Shorter ball, down the leg side. The umpire signals a wide ball for negative bowling.
Fuller ball, on middle. Usman Khawaja leans and blocks it out.
Shorter ball, around the leg pole. Usman Khawaja defends it out.
Tad fuller, down the leg side. Usman Khawaja keeps it away with his pads.
Tad shorter, down the leg side. Usman Khawaja defends it towards square leg.
Tad shorter, outside off. Usman Khawaja punches it through cover for a brace.
Fuller now, down leg. Usman Khawaja pads it away.
Flighted ball, on leg. Steven Smith keeps it out.
Flighted again, on leg. Steven Smith stays solid in his defence.
Down leg, Steven Smith kicks it away.
On off, blocked out.
Full and on off, pushed towards covers.
Full once again, around off. Steven Smith defends it towards cover.
Full, and quicker this time on middle. Usman Khawaja hangs back and defends it out.
Quick again, spraying it on the pads. Usman Khawaja works it away towards square leg and rotates the strike.
Shorter ball, spinning it in, around off. Steven Smith knocks it to long off for a single.
Firing it on the pads, quicker and flatter. Usman Khawaja clips it towards square leg for a single.
Fuller ball, outside off. Steven Smith defends it out.
Loopy ball, full, outside off. Steven Smith leans and defends this one.
Loopy ball, outside off. Usman Khawaja gets down on his knee and looks to sweep this, but gets an inside edge onto his pads.
Tad shorter, outside off. Usman Khawaja taps it towards point for a single.
Tosses it up, full, outside off. Steven Smith presses forward and blocks it out solidly.
Another flighted delivery, full again, around middle. Steven Smith eases it down to long on and rotates the strike.
Tosses it up again, around off. Usman Khawaja sweeps it towards square leg for a single.
Loopy delivery, full and on middle. Steven Smith defends it out.
Fuller ball, outside off, at 85.4 clicks. Usman Khawaja pushes it towards point.
Full ball, around off. Usman Khawaja defends this one.
Shorter ball, wide of off. Usman Khawaja cuts it past point. Hasan Ali chases the ball, dives forward, and keeps the ball away from the ropes. 3 runs taken!
Loopy ball, full, on middle. Steven Smith leans and defends it out.
Fuller ball again, around middle. Steven Smith works it away towards long on for a single.
Pitches this one up, outside off. Usman Khawaja taps it toward point for a single.
Babar Azam begins with a flatter ball, outside off. Usman Khawaja pushes it towards point and rotates the strike.
Loopy ball, very full, around middle. Steven Smith digs it out back to the bowler.
Fuller, outside off. Steven Smith defends it out.
Slower through the air, full, around middle. Steven Smith leans and blocks it out.
Full again, around the fourth stump line. Steven Smith flicks it towards long on and rotates the strike.
Another fuller ball, turning away, outside off. Usman Khawaja drives it to the fielder at cover.
Azhar Ali begins with a full toss, on the body. Steven Smith whips it towards deep mid-wicket for a single.
Slower through the air, outside off, fuller ball. Usman Khawaja blocks it out.
Very full again, outside off, tosses it up. Usman Khawaja drives it past cover for a brace.
Azhar Ali misses his length again, serves a full toss ball, around off. Usman Khawaja knocks it to long off for a single.
Loopy ball, spraying it down the leg side. Steven Smith works it away towards square leg for a single.
Turning it back in, around middle. Usman Khawaja blocks it out off the back foot.
Spinning it in on middle, tad fuller. Steven Smith works it away towards square leg for a single.
Fuller now, around middle and leg. Usman Khawaja defends it out.
Firing it down the leg side, tad shorter. Usman Khawaja misses his flick.
Fullish ball, on the pads. Usman Khawaja blocks it out.
Firing it down leg, fullish ball. Usman Khawaja blocks it out easily.
Outside this time, turning away, fuller ball. Usman Khawaja leans and drives it towards cover.
Tosses it up, fuller ball, outside off. Steven Smith drives it to long off for a single.

No ball! A huge full toss! Azhar Ali misses his length and serves a full toss, almost at chest height, around off. Usman Khawaja pulls it towards deep mid-wicket for a single. No ball called for height!
Fuller now, around middle. Steven Smith pushes it towards long on for a single.
Loopy ball, full, on off. Usman Khawaja leans and defends it out.
Another full toss, on the pads. Usman Khawaja flicks it towards mid-wicket for a single.
Tosses it up, full, outside off. Steven Smith leans and defends it out.
Another loopy delivery, outside off. Steven Smith leaves it alone.
The crowd erupts as Shaheen Afridi hurls in with the new cherry. He bowls a length ball, outside off. Usman Khawaja lets it sail through.
On a length, outside off. No swing movement still. Usman Khawaja lets it be.

NOT OUT! Good-length ball, outside off, moving away. Usman Khawaja tries to chop it away but the ball stays a touch low and it goes past the inside edge. Half an appeal for caught behind but there was nothing on it. However, Mohammad Rizwan is keen on taking a review and they do go for it. UltraEdge shows nothing. A poor review by Pakistan!
Length ball, on off. Usman Khawaja covers the line and keeps it out.
Length ball going down the leg side. Usman Khawaja misses his glance.
On a good length, on middle. Usman Khawaja hops and works it on the leg side. A maiden!

FOUR! Welcome boundary for Australia and Steven Smith! Ashraf bowls a half volley, on middle and leg. Steven Smith shows full face of the bat and drives it to long on for a boundary. First boundary in nearly 23 overs reckons Mike Haysman on air.
On a length, outside off. Steven Smith lets it sail through.
Touch fuller, outside off. Steven Smith lets it be.
On a length, around off. Steven Smith taps it to point.
Back of a length, on off. Steven Smith punches it towards covers off the back foot.
Fuller in length this time, on off. Smith drives it to mid off.
On a length, on off. Usman Khawaja stands tall and blocks it right under his eyes.
Full and on middle, blocked out by Uzzie.
On a good length, on middle. Usman Khawaja covers the line and defends.

Fuller in length, tailing back in, on leg. Usman Khawaja misses his flick and gets struck on the pads. Shaheen Afridi appeals for an lbw but Aleem Dar says no. Replay shows that there was an inside edge onto the pads.
Very full, on off. Usman Khawaja drives it back to the bowler.

FOUR! A loosener from Shaheen Afridi! Sprays this on the pads and Usman Khawaja accepts this gift with both hands and flicks it behind square on the leg side for a boundary. 150-run stand comes up as well between these two.
Full and on middle, blocked out.
Length ball, on off. Steven Smith presses forward and blocks it out watchfully.
Touch fuller, outside off. Steven Smith keeps it out to the off side.
Smith drives this full ball to mid off.
Short of a length, on off. Steven Smith defends off the back foot.
Short of a length, outside off. Steven Smith dabs it towards the slip cordon.
Length ball, on off. Usman Khawaja plays a perfect defensive shot.
Short of a length, outside off. Punched towards covers for a single.
Good-length ball, on middle. Steven Smith gets behind the ball and defends it out.
Fuller, outside off. Smith pushes it to mid off and scampers through.
Swing and a miss! Better line from Afridi! Bowls it full, outside off. Usman Khawaja reaches out and tries to drive but misses.
A low full toss, outside off. Usman Khawaja keeps it out.
Full and on middle, worked on the leg side.
On a length, outside off. Left alone.
Length, outside off. Smith covers the line and blocks it out.

FOUR! Beautiful shot! Exquisite timing on that one. Fuller in length, outside off. Steven Smith leans and caresses it through covers. The ball races away to the fence. Classical cover-drive. You can watch it all day!
Short of a length, on off. Steven Smith blocks it out.
An action replay of the previous delivery! Shortish, on off. Smith keeps it out.
On a length, outside off. Usman Khawaja leaves it alone.
Another length ball, shaping away, outside off. Usman Khawaja offers no shot.
Back of a length, outside off, at 135.3 clicks. Usman Khawaja shoulders his arms at it.
Length ball, outside off. Usman Khawaja defends it off the front foot.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Usman Khawaja defends it out.
Beaten! Back of a length now, outside off, shaping away. Usman Khawaja stays in his crease and looks to have a poke at it but misses.
Flatter ball, on middle. Steven Smith blocks it out.
Loopy ball, outside off, extra bounce as well. Smith lets it go.
Flatter on middle, Smith keeps it out.
Full and on leg, Smith lunges forward and defends it back to the bowler.
Full and on middle, pushed back to the bowler again.
Tossed up, on off. Smith defends it to the off side. A maiden!
On a length, outside off. Usman Khawaja pushes it towards mid off and scampers through the other end for a single.
Outside off, on a length. Steven Smith leaves it alone.
Good-length delivery, around off. Steven Smith defends it out.
Length ball, nipping back in from outside off. Steven Smith lets it sail through.

OUT! CAUGHT! A wicket at the stroke of Stumps. Absolute stunner from Faheem Ashraf! What a catch from him late in the day. Steven Smith has to depart after a fine knock of 72. Hasan Ali with a short-of-a-length delivery, outside off, shaping away. Steven Smith goes for a back foot punch but the ball nicks off the outside edge and flies to Faheem Ashraf at second slip. Good reflexes from him as he takes it with his left hand diving that side. He grabbed it inches from the ground but the umpire wants to be sure and he takes it upstairs. After a couple of replays from multiple angles, the third umpire rules the decision in favor of Pakistan. This will lift the spirit of Pakistan and Hasan Ali has got his man.
Howout: c Faheem Ashraf b Hasan Ali

Commentary: Brilliant from Hasan Ali! Bowls a yorker now to the night watcman but Nathan Lyon does well to dig it out.
Fuller, outside off. Usman Khawaja leans onto it and drives it through covers for a single.
Length ball down the leg side. Nathan Lyon leaves it comfortably.
Length ball, angling in, on middle from 'round the wicket. Nathan Lyon works it to deep square leg but the batters doesn't take a single.
A yorker, on middle. Lyon jams it out.
Length ball from over the wicket, outside off. Lyon lets it sail through.

A dot to end! Nathan Lyon has done well to counter the last five balls of the day! A nervy moment on this delivery though! Short of a length, on middle. Nathan Lyon tucks it straight to Imam-ul-Haq at short leg. However, Imam-ul-Haq took his eyes off as the ball was coming at him. The ball hit him right in the knee area. A wicket in the penultimate over of Stumps and a dropped catch on the last ball. THAT WILL BE STUMPS ON DAY 1!
Hasan Ali begins with a length ball, outside off, shaping away. Usman Khawaja leaves it alone.
Another good-length delivery, nipping back in, outside off, at 136 clicks. Usman Khawaja offers no shot to that.
On a length, outside off. Usman Khawaja shoulders his arms at it.
Much fuller this time, outside off. Usman Khawaja drives to the fielder at cover.
Angling in on the pads, fuller in length. Usman Khawaja works it towards mid-wicket.
Length delivery, outside off. Usman Khawaja does not fiddle with it. A maiden to begin with!

Shaheen Afridi goes 'round the wicket, serves a fuller ball, outside off. Nathan Lyon pushes it past point. Sajid Khan chases it and keeps the ball away from the ropes. Two taken! First runs of the day! Nathan Lyon gets off the mark as well!
On a length, around middle. Nathan Lyon stays in his crease and defends it out.
Another good-length delivery, around middle, at 134.6 clicks. Nathan Lyon blocks it out.
Fuller this time, outside off. Nathan Lyon drives and finds the fielder at cover.
Shaheen Afridi serves a fuller ball again, from over the wicket, around off. Nathan Lyon pushes it with the inner half of his bat back to the bowler.
Shorter ball now, around middle. Nathan Lyon pulls it towards deep square leg for a single. He retains the strike.

NOT OUT! A loud shout for LBW, but the umpire says no! Good-length delivery, tailing back in onto the pads. Nathan Lyon looks to flick but misses and gets rapped on his front pad. Hasan Ali convinces Babar Azam to for the review. The replay rolls in and UltraEdge confirms no bat involved. Ball Tracker indicates it is the umpire's call on wickets hitting. The on-field decision stands.
On a length, outside off. Nathan Lyon pushes it towards cover.
Outside off, on a length. Nathan Lyon stays in his crease and taps it towards point.
Tad fuller now, outside off. Nathan Lyon pushes it towards mid off.
Full length, on off. Nathan Lyon pushes it to mid off.
FOUR! Edgy! A length ball, outside off. Nathan Lyon looks to chase it. The ball races away to the fine leg fence off the inside edge. Lyon with some luck on his side now.
Good-length delivery, outside off, at 139.6 clicks. Usman Khawaja leans and defends it out.
FOUR! Perfect timing! Fuller ball, angling in, around middle and leg. Usman Khawaja uses his wrists and flicks it past mid-wicket for a boundary.
On a length, outside off. Usman Khawaja leans and defends it towards cover.
Back of a length, down the leg side. Usman Khawaja tucks it towards square leg and rotates the strike.
Shaheen Afridi goes 'round the wicket to the right-hander, serves a fuller ball, drifting into the pads. Nathan Lyon clips it towards deep square leg for a single.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Usman Khawaja stays in his crease and looks to blocks this but the ball goes off the outside edge towards the fielder at gully who collects it on the bounce.
Back of a length, outside off, shaping away a tad. Nathan Lyon looks to defend but misses and the ball zips past his outside edge.
On a length now, jagging back in, around middle. Nathan Lyon defends it out.
Another length delivery, around middle. Nathan Lyon defends it out.
Outside off, on a length. Nathan Lyon stays back and cuts it towards point.
Fuller ball this time, angling in on the pads. Nathan Lyon flicks it towards deep mid-wicket and rotates the strike!
Change of angle now! Hasan Ali goes 'round the wicket and delivers a length ball, outside off. Usman Khawaja taps it towards point.
FOUR! Nathan Lyon gets his second boundary of the innings now. It is a short ball, on the bodyline. Nathan Lyon swivels and pulls it to fine leg for a boundary. Lyon rides the bounce really well.
Slightly short and on off, angled into the batter. Lyon swivels on the back foot, pulls it to deep mid-wicket. Faheem Ashraf runs to his left and saves a certain boundary. They take two.

Back of a length, some extra bounce off the deck. Nathan Lyon hangs back, tries to hook it away but only connects with thin air. Shaheen Afridi thinks there is some sound on it. He raises his finger but the umpire does not replicate his action. Nothing from the keeper as well.
Short ball, on off. Nathan Lyon pulls it to deep mid-wicket. Hasan Ali makes a sharp stop in the deep. They take two.
Another short one, angled into the body, in this over. Nathan Lyon stays back and pulls it fine on the leg side for a single. A good over for Australia.
NO BALL! A length ball, on the fifth stump. Usman Khawaja leaves it alone for the keeper. The umpire signals a no ball, as the bowler oversteps.
Now, Afridi is done with his over. Length ball, outside off. Usman Khawaja has not stroke to offer. 10 runs off the over. Pakistan have hardly found any movement with a fairly new ball.
Fuller, on middle and leg. Lyon tucks it to mid-wicket.
Floated, full, on the pads. Lyon clips it to mid-wicket with ease.
FOUR! Nathan Lyon picking up his pace here. Fuller, on off. Lyon gets low and sweeps it through mid-wicket with great control. Races away to the boundary line.
Another sweep shot comes out to a full delivery, Lyon is happy with a single.
Looped up, outside off, turns in a bit. Usman Khawaja stays back to defend it to the off side.
Fuller, outside off. Usman Khawaja leans in and pushes it to cover. 5 runs off it. Ali yet to bag a wicket.

FOUR! Nathan Lyon is not going to sit back at all! He is on the charge here. Afridi starts with a short ball, angled into the ribs. Lyon hangs back and pulls it through square leg for a boundary. The night watchman scoring so freely can be frustrating for the hosts.
Short ball, on off. Lyon pulls it to deep mid-wicket for one.
Usman Khawaja rotates the strike now! An inswinging yorker, angled into the pads. Usman Khawaja rocks back and tucks it to the leg side for one.
Back of a length, on the body. Lyon heaves it across the line to square leg for one.
Full length, outside off. Usman Khawaja leaves it alone, as the ball dies towards the keeper.
A yorker now, on off. Usman Khawaja gets his blade down in time. Digs it out back to the bowler. Runs are coming in at a brisk rate for Australia.
Slower one, full and outside off. Lyon eases it to cover for a quick single.
Tossed up, outside off. It grips and turns in. Usman Khawaja gets low and tries to sweep it away but gets betean completely. A rare false shot by him.
On off, defended to short leg.

NOT OUT! Pakistan lose a review here. Babar Azam took it more in hope. Tossed up, around off. Usman Khawaja sets himself up and goes for the reverse sweep. Although he fails to get any bat on it. The ball hit the back leg and goes to the left of Babar Azam at first slip, who grabs it cleanly and later, puts in an appeal. The umpire is unmoved. Babar Azam takes a review after a lot of thinking. The UltraEdge confirms no bat is involved. The Ball Tracking confirms the ball is pitching outside the line. Usman Khawaja survives.
Slower through the air, fuller, around middle. Usman Khawaja works it away towards mid-wicket.
Darting it on the pads, fuller ball. Usman Khawaja flicks it towards deep square leg for a single.
Faheem Ashraf starts with a full-length delivery, outside off. Usman Khawaja drives and finds the fielder at mid off.
A length ball, angled into the pads. Usman Khawaja blocks it to the leg side.
Length ball, on off, blocked out.
Good length, on off. Usman Khawaja defends it out solidly.

FOUR! Usman Khawaja gets lucky here. A length ball, around off. The ball dies as it reaches the batter. Usman Khawaja gets squared up, as he tries to defend it out. It takes the outside edge and races down to third man for a boundary.
Back of a length, around off. Usman Khawaja defends it out watchfully. A good over by Faheem Ashraf.
Loopy ball, full in length, outside off. Nathan Lyon pushes it back to the bowler.
Tosses it up, full again, around middle. Nathan Lyon lunges and blocks it out solidly.
Slower through the air, outside off, full in length. Nathan Lyon sweeps and finds the fielder at square leg.
On the pads this time, pitches it up. Nathan Lyon flicks it towards the short leg. The ball hits the pads of the fielder there!
Loopy ball, sliding down the leg side. Nathan Lyon leaves it alone and Mohammad Rizwan collects the ball nicely.
Drifting down leg, tad fuller. Nathan Lyon stays in his crease and flicks it towards square leg for a single.
On a length, angling in on middle. Nathan Lyon clips it to mid-wicket.

Mix-up...but no harm done! Fuller ball, around middle. Nathan Lyon shows the full face of his bat and pushes it gently straight down the ground. He leaves his crease to sneak in a quick single. But Usman Khawaja sends him back mid-way. Shaheen Afridi from mid on, dives and collects the ball and throws it towards the keeper, but Nathan Lyon is back in safely!
Another fuller ball, around middle. Nathan Lyon drives it towards mid on.

DROPPED! Return catch but does not stick! Slower ball now, fuller in length, around off. Nathan Lyon drives it uppishly towards the left of the bowler. Faheem Ashraf sticks his left hand out but fails to grab it.

FOUR! Perfect execution! This can be so frustrating for Pakistan! Good batting from Nathan Lyon! On a length, outside off. Nathan Lyon hangs back, opens the face of the bat, and guides it past gully for a boundary.
Angling it on the pads, tad fuller. Nathan Lyon flicks it towards square leg for a single.
Very full, around off. Nathan Lyon drives it towards mid off.
Darting it on the pads, fullish again. Nathan Lyon works it away towards fine leg for a single.
Loopy ball, spinning back in, fuller ball. Usman Khawaja pushes it towards cover.
Fuller, outside off. Usman Khawaja prods and blocks it solidly.
Beaten! Straighter ball now, outside off. Usman Khawaja leans to defend it, but he gets beaten on the outside edge.
Fullish delivery, turning back in, on the pads. Usman Khawaja plays it with the turn and clips it towards square leg for a single.
Shorter ball, on teh bodyline. Usman Khawaja swivels and pulls it towards deep square leg. Single taken!
An appeal for LBW, but the umpire is unmoved! A fuller ball, angling it onto the pads. Nathan Lyon looks to flick but misses and gets hit on his pads. That looked like it was sliding down leg.
On a length now, around middle. Nathan Lyon gets on toes and blocks it out..
Slower ball now, fuller ball, around middle. Nathan Lyon knocks it to mid on.

Length ball, angling back in, around off. Nathan Lyon looks to push this away, but the ball goes off the inside edge back onto the deck. The ball bounces back and it sticks between Nathan Lyon's elbow.
Back of a length, around off. Nathan Lyon pushes it towards cover.
Fuller ball, turning in on middle. Usman Khawaja sweeps it towards deep square leg for a single.
Fuller again, around middle. Nathan Lyon flicks it to mid-wicket.
Touch short, outside off. Nathan Lyon dabs it towards point.
A full toss now, around middle. Nathan Lyon gets low and sweeps it towards mid-wicket, who makes a good stop diving to his right.
Loopy ball, full, outside off. Nathan Lyon gets down on his knee and sweeps it past square leg for a single.
Turning it in, around middle, tad shorter. Usman Khawaja flicks it towards square leg.

A nice delivery by Faheem Ashraf. A good-length ball, outside off. It nips in sharply off the deck. Nathan Lyon is caught high on his pads inside the crease, as he looks to flick it away. Mohammad Rizwan grabs the ball behind the stumps and throws it in the air. Everyone had eyes on him, but he gathers the ball and tells the bowler that it was very high.

OUT! TIMBER! Faheem Ashraf comes up with a peach of a delivery to get rid of Nathan Lyon. Ashraf serves an inswinging delivery, on a fuller length, around middle and leg. Nathan Lyon hangs back and tries to flick it away, but ends up playing all around it. The ball goes through to rattle the stumps. Faheem Ashraf gets the first wicket on Day 2. Can Pakistan take one more before Lunch?
Howout: b Faheem Ashraf

Commentary: Faheem Ashraf comes 'round the wicket now. Fuller, angled in on off. Head defends it out solidly.
Length ball, outside off. Head leaves it alone for the keeper.

FOUR! Some width on offer and Head makes the most off it. He gets off the mark in some fine fashion. It is a short ball, outside off. Travis Head hangs back, cuts it hard through point. It races away to the boundary. This is his bread and butter! You cannot give any width to Head.
This is much better from Ashraf. A length ball, angled in, around off. Head stays back and defends it out watchfully. A wicket taking over of Faheem Ashraf comes to an end.
Floated, full and around off. Usman Khawaja leans in to defend it out but gets beaten on the outside edge.
Around off, Usman Khawaja blocks it out watchfully.
Fuller, on middle and leg. Usman Khawaja goes back to defend it out.
Fuller, on the stumps. Usman Khawaja remains solid in his defense.
Tosses it up, fuller ball, around middle. Usman Khawaja knocks it down to long off for a single.

An appeal for lbw but the umpire is unmoved. It is angled in, full and outside off. Travis Head presses forward, looks to defend it out but missses. He gets hit on his pads. The impact looked outside the line. Hence, Babar Azam did not opt for the last review.
Back of a length, outside off. Usman Khawaja shuffles across and shoulders his arms.
Short ball, outside off. Usman Khawaja pushes it to point for a single.
Full length, outside off. Head taps it to point.
Faheem Ashraf serves it full, on the off stumps. Travis Head walks out of the crease and drives it down the ground. Faheem Ashraf manages to get a finger on it, kills the pace of the ball.
Length ball, on off, defended out.

Full length, on middle and leg. Travis Head flicks it to the left of mid on. Nauman Ali moves to his left, dives and makes a brilliant stop. Looks like the Pakistan players are energised after that wicket of Lyon.
Short and outside off. Usman Khawaja cuts it through point. The fielder gives it a chase and does enough to keep it inside the boundary line. The batters take three.
Full, on off, blocked back to the bowler.
Flatter, outside off. Head works it to the off side.
Tossed up, on off. Head pushes it back to the bowler.
Quicker, fuller, on off. Head defends it out watchfully.
BEATEN! Tossed up, full, outside off. Head leans but fails to defend it out. It zips past his outside edge.
Good length, outside off. Left alone by Usman Khawaja.
Full length, angled down leg. Well away from Usman Khawaja's reach.
An attempted bouncer, but it dies in the middle of the deck. The ball takes a while to reach the keeper. Usman Khawaja ducks under it. He had to get vry low to let the ball go above him.
Outside off, left alone.
Full length, outside off. Usman Khawaja pushes it to cover.
A maiden for Hasan Ali now! A full-length ball, outside off. Usman Khawaja pushes it to cover.
Quicker one, spinning away a tad, on middle. Travis Head hangs back and pushes it back to the bowler.
Much fuller now, on the pads. Travis Head works it towards mid on scampers through to the other end.
Loopy ball, full and outside off, at 83.9 clicks. Usman Khawaja presses forward and defends it out.
Loopy ball, on middle. Usman Khawaja leans and defends it out.
Short this time, turning away, outside off. Usman Khawaja cuts it towards point and runs across to the other end. Btu sloppy work from the fielder there allows the batters to take another run.
Fuller ball, outside off. Usman Khawaja leans and taps it towards cover for a single.

On a length, darting it on the thigh pads. Usman Khawaja tucks it towards fine leg for a single. That will be 150 for Usman Khawaja! He continues to shine! He is the third Australian opener to score 150 against Pakistan!
FOUR! Fraction shorter, wide of off. Travis Head stays in his crease and slashes past point for a boundary.
On a length, outside off. Travis Head dabs it towards point.
Fuller now, around middle. Travis Head knocks it to mid on.
Fullish again,a round middle. Travis Head once again drives and finds the fielder at mid on.
FOUR! Oh, shot! On a length, outside off. Travis Head waits for it and chops it late, past gully for a glorious boundary.
Quicker now, around middle. Usman Khawaja hangs back and defends it out.
Fullish again, around off. Usman Khawaja leans and defends it out towards point.
Fuller again, turning away, around off. Usman Khawaja stays in his crease and pushes it towards cover for a single.
Shorter now, around middle. Travis Head pushes it to mid-wicket off the back foot.
Fraction shorter again, around off. Travis Head punches it onto the off side off the back foot. Silly point fielder gets hit there!
Tad quicker, around middle, fuller ball. Travis Head blocks it out.
Fuller ball, around middle. Usman Khawaja eases it down to long on for a single.
Shortish delivery, outside off. Travis Head leaves it alone.
Loopy ball this time, outside off, full in length. Travis Head lunges and looks to defend this but gets an inside edge back onto his pads.
Quicker, spinning it in, outside off. Travis Head stays in his crease and pushes it towards point.
Much fuller now, around middle. Travis Head works it towards mid-wicket.
Flighted delivery, outside off. Travis Head leans and blocks it out.
Much quicker now, firing it on middle. Usman Khawaja stays back and defends it out. Good pace on this one!
Slower now, full, around middle. Usman Khawaja leans and scoops it towards fine leg for a brace.
Fuller again, around the fourth stump line. Usman Khawaja defends it out.
Slower through the air now, around middle and off, fuller ball. Usman Khawaja leans and blocks it out.
Quicker now, this on lands around middle and turns away a tad. Usman Khawaja stays back and pushes it towards cover.
Fullish, around off. Usman Khawaja drives it to the fielder at extra cover.
Shorter ball, spinning it in on middle. Travis Head hangs back and taps it towards mid-wicket.
Fuller ball, around off. Travis Head defends it out.
Slower through the air, full, around middle. Travis Head sweeps it towards square leg for a single.
Another loopy ball, around middle. Usman Khawaja gets down on his knee and sweeps it towards mid-wicket and rotates the strike!
Almost chopped on! Fullish ball turning back in, around off. Travis Head hangs back and tries to cut this, but the ball goes off the inside edge just past the leg pole.
Quicker now, outside off, shortish ball. Travis Head stays in his crease and slashes it towards point. Hasan Ali there dives to his right and makes a good stop.
Loopy ball, full, on middle. Usman Khawaja leans and defends it out watchfully.
Full again, around middle. Usman Khawaja blocks it out solidly.
Fuller again, outside off this time. Usman Khawaja lunges and pushes it to cover.
Slightly full again, around off. Usman Khawaja pushes it back to the bowler.
Much quicker this time, around middle, fuller ball. Usman Khawaja stays in his crease and does well to defend this one.
Tosses it up, outside off, full in length. Usman Khawaja pushes it to cover. A maiden to end the first session! That will be Lunch on Day 2!
Shaheen Afridi begins with an inswinging yorker, on middle. Travis Head digs it out towards mid on.
Angling in once again, very full, around off. Travis Head drives it with the bottom half of his bat towards mid off.
On a length now, down the leg side. Travis Head leaves it alone.
Good ball! Fuller ball, swinging back in around middle. Travis Head taps it towards mid-wicket.
Another length ball, angling in around middle, at 140.3 clicks. Travis Head tucks it to mid-wicket once again. Good signs for Pakistan as the ball is reversing!
Shorter now, wide of off. Travis Head cuts it towards deep point for a single.
Fuller ball, around middle. Travis Head tucks it towards square leg.
Loopy ball, outside off, full in length. Travis Head leans and defends it out.
Quicker now, around off, fullish ball. Travis Head pushes it towards mid off.
FOUR! First boundary of the second session! Slower now, loopy delivery, around middle. Travis Head shimmies down the pitch and drills it past mid off for a boundary.
Loopy delivery again, on middle, fuller ball. Travis Head drives and finds the fielder at mid off.
Flatter, quicker, outside off. Travis Head dabs it to point.

FOUR BYES! Bonus runs for Australia! Fuller ball, angling down leg. Usman Khawaja leaves it alone. Mohammad Rizwan dives to his right, tries to grab the ball, but the ball defects off his gloves and goes towards the fence for a boundary.
Tad fuller, around the off pole. Usman Khawaja defends it out off the front foot.
On a length now, around middle. Usman Khawaja presents the full face of the bat and defends it out.
Yorker-length delivery, outside off, at 143 clicks. Usman Khawaja opens the face of his bat and guides it past point for a brace.
Shaping back in, around off, on a good length, at 140.2 clicks. Usman Khawaja blocks it out solidly.
Well bowled! Another yorker, swinging in around middle. Usman Khawaja does well to get his bat down in time and dig it out.
FOUR! Top shot! Short and outside off. Travis Head hangs back and cuts it hard through point for a boundary.

OUT! LBW! Sajid Khan gets on to drop in front of Travis Head. He appeals for an lbw and the umpire agrees. Travis Head thinks it might to going down leg and takes the review. It is a fuller ball, on middle and leg. Travis Head prods and tries to defend it out but hits his pads instead. This allows the ball to hit his front pad. The UltraEdge shows no bat involved. The Ball Tracking shows that it is the umpire's call on the ball hitting the wickets. A great start to the post-Lunch session for Pakistan.
Howout: lbw b Sajid Khan

Commentary: Fuller ball, turning back in, around middle. Cameron Green stays back and defends it out.
Quicker now, around middle. Cameron Green once again, hands back and blocks it out.
Flatter ball, full, around middle. Cameron Green lunges and blocks it towards short leg.
Tad shorter, aroun middle. Cameron Green stays in his crease and works it away past the short leg fielder.
A full-length delivery, tailing into the pads. Usman Khawaja defends it out to the leg side.
Another one angled into the pads. Usman Khawaja tucks it to mid-wicket.
Full length, on the stumps. Usman Khawaja defends it out watchfully.
Length ball, outside off, this one moves away from the batter. Usman Khawaja is happy to leave it alone.
Five dots on the trot! Full length, outside off, Afridi makes this one to move away as well. Usman Khawaja defends it out solidly.
A great delivery to end the over. A yorker now that tails in ferociuosly. Usman Khawaja digs it out brilliantly. Only a set batter could have dealt with it.
Vey full, around middle. Cameron Green defends it out.
Tosses it up, full, around middle, spinning back in. Cameron Green leans and defends it out.
Fuller again, outside off. Cameron Green blocks it out.
Shorter ball, around middle. Cameron Green stays in his crease and knocks it to long on for a single.
On off, blocked back to the bowler.
Looped up, full and on off. Usman Khawaja prods and blocks it out.
Full in length, outside off. Cameron Green leans and drives it to the fielder at cover.
Bye! On a length, down the leg side. Cameron Green looks to flick but misses. Mohammad Rizwan dives and failed to stop it. The collect a bye.
Swinging in on middle, very full. Usman Khawaja drives it towards mid off.
Yorker-length delivery, angling in, around middle. Usman Khawaja once again does well to squeeze it out.
Shaheen Afridi misses his length, serves a full toss, down the leg side. Usman Khawaja leaves it alone. Mohammad Rizwan dives to his right and grabs the ball with his right hand. Good stop by him!
Shorter ball, around middle. Usman Khawaja ducks underneath it.
Fuller ball, around middle and leg. Cameron Green tucks it towards short leg.
Tad slower now, full, around middle. Cameron Green advances down the pitch and pushes it towards mid on.

Mic-up...but no harm down! A fuller ball, spinning back in, around middle. Cameron Green taps it towards square leg. Usman Khawaja from the other end leaves his crease for a single. But he is sent back halfway. The fielder there throws the ball towards the bowler, but Usman Khawaja dives and makes his ground!
Shorter ball, spinning in around middle. Cameron Green defends it out solidly.
Fuller ball, around middle, quicker as well. Cameron Green defends it out solidly.
Darting it around the off pole, quick again. Cameron Green stays in his crease and blocks it out.
Fuller ball, down the leg side. Usman Khawaja clips it towards square leg for a single.
