FOUR! Streaky! On a length, outside off, shaping away a tad. Cameron Green looks to defend but the ball goes off the outside edge past gully for a boundary!
Good-length delivery, outside off. Cameron Green leaves it alone.
Another length delivery, outside off. Cameron Green offers no shot to that.
Full this time, outside off. Cameron Green drives it towards mid off and scampers through to the other end.
Length ball, angling in on middle, around off. Usman Khawaja defends it out.
Fuller ball, around middle. Cameron Green leans and blocks it out.
Loopy ball again, full, around middle. Cameron Green blocks it out.
Turning in, around middle, shorter this time. Cameron Green pushes it towards cover off the back foot.
Tosses this one up, full in length, around off. Cameron Green defends it out solidly.
Flighted delivery, around middle. Cameron Green advances down the pitch and pushes it back to the bowler.
Tosses it up, full, around off. Cameron Green defends it out.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Usman Khawaja pushes it past point and takes a single.
Hasan Ali goes over the wicket to the right-hander, serves a fullish ball, outside off. Cameron Green drives it towards cover for a single.
Full, angling in around middle. Usman Khawaja nudges it towards mid-wicket.
Fullish delivery, around off. Usman Khawaja leans and blocks it out.
Fuller again, angling in on the pads. Usman Khawaja flicks it to square leg.
A yorker now, around middle, at around 138 clicks. Usman Khawaja digs it out.
Fuller ball, quicker again, around middle. Cameron Green defends it out.
Slower through the air, full again, around middle. Cameron Green blocks it out.
Flighted ball, full, around middle. Cameron Green has defended this off the back foot.
Quicker again, outside off, full again. Cameron Green stays in his crease and tries to cut this but gets an inside edge onto the deck towards first slip.
Full again, on middle. Cameron Green skips down the pitch and defends it out.
Flatter ball, around middle. Cameron Green miscues his time to mid off.
A low full toss, around middle. Usman Khawaja drives it towards to cover.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Usman Khawaja drives it towards mid off.
Another length delivery, angling in around off. Usman Khawaja taps it towards cover-point for a single.
Fuller ball, tailing back in, around off. Cameron Green drives and finds the fielder at mid off.
Full again, angling in on the pads. Cameron Green flicks it past square leg. The fielder runs to his right and stops the ball with his leg to keep the ball away from the ropes. Two taken!
On a length, outside off. Cameron Green blocks it out off the front foot.
Beaten! A ripper! Fuller ball, sinning away, outside off. Usman Khawaja tries to block this but gets beaten on the outside edge.

OUT! CLEANED HIM UP! Sajid Khan strikes once again and gets the big wicket of Usman Khawaja! A masterclass innings comes to an end! A dream delivery for an off-spinner! Fuller ball, this one lands around middle and turns away. Usman Khawaja stays in his crease and looks to block this but gets beaten as the ball spins away from him and knocks the off stump. Usman Khawaja walks back to a standing ovation! Pakistan have done well in this session!
Howout: b Sajid Khan

Commentary: Loopy ball, full in length, around middle. Alex Carey leans and defends it out.
Full again, around middle. Alex Carey leans and sweeps it towards fine leg for a brace. He gets off the mark with that!
Another fuller ball, around middle, slower through the air. This time Alex Carey gets low and rever-sweeps it towards point. Single taken! Brave batting from Alex Carey!
Loopy ball, outside off, fuller ball. Cameron Green drives it towards mid off.

Swing and a miss! A length ball, shaping away, outside off. Alex Carey tries to drive this away from hs body, but misses! Mohammad Rizwan grabs the ball and throws it in the air! There was definitely no edge on that! Hasan Ali walks to Rizwan and hugs him. Pakistan are really pumped now!
Fuller now, outside off. Alex Carey pushes it towards cover.
On a length now, around the fifth stump line. Alex Carey defends it out off the back foot.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Alex Carey leaves it alone.
Angling in on the pads, on a length. Alex Carey blocks it towards mid-wicket.
Change of angle now! Hasan Ali goes over the wicket, serves a length ball, around middle. Alex Carey defends it out. A maiden over!
Loopy ball, around middle, full in length. Cameron Green lunges and blocks it out.
Slower through the air again, full and around middle. Cameron Green defends it out.
Full, around middle. Cameron Green skips down the pitch and knocks it past mid on for a single.
Slower through the air, on middle. Alex Carey presses forward and defends it out.
Full in length, outside off, slower again. Alex Carey drives it wide of mid off and takes a single.
Loopy delivery, on middle, full in length. Cameron Green presses forward and blocks it out.
Faheem Ashraf begins with a length ball, outside off. Alex Carey blocks it out solidly.
Angling in around middle, on a length. Alex Carey defends this one.
Swinging in, fuller ball, around middle and leg. Alex Carey nudges it towards mid-wicket.
Slower ball now, on a length, around middle. Alex Carey defends it towards point.
Yorker now, outside off, slower again at 118.1 clicks. Alex Carey jams it out towards point.
Back of a length, angling in on middle. Alex Carey taps it towards miid-wicket. a good over from Faheem Ashraf! A maiden for him!
Shorter ball, turning in, around middle. Cameron Green hangs back and pushes it towards mid on.
Much fuller ball now, outside off. Cameron Green flicks it towards square leg for a single.
Slower through the air, full, around middle. Alex Carey lunges and defends it out.
Full again, outside off. Alex Carey drives it towards extra cover.
Slower through the air, on middle, fuller ball. Alex Carey presses forward and blocks it out.
FOUR! Some aggression by Alex Carey now! Good shot this from him! A fuller ball, around middle. Alex Carey advances down the pitch and smashes it over the bowler's head for a boundary.
Fuller ball, around middle. Cameron Green punches this to mid on.
Full in length, angling in on the pads. Cameron Green flicks it towards deep square leg for a brace.
Fullish again, swinging back in on middle. Cameron Green whips it towards square leg for a single this time.
On a length now, outside off. Alex Carey leaves it alone.
good-length delivery again, outside off. Alex Carey strokes it towards cover for a single.
Fraction shorter, outside off. Alex Carey pushes it off the back foot towards the bowler.

A huge mix-up! Fuller, outside off. Cameron Green pushes it to the off side. It looked like an easy single but a miscommunication made it horrible for the batters. In the end, both were able to get back safely.
Fuller, outside off, blocked out.
Floated, around off. Green defends it out watchfully.
Full, on the pads, Green clips it to fine leg for a brace.
Fuller, outside off, blocked out.
Full, on the stumps, Green blocks it out watchfully.
Back of a length, outside off. Alex Carey hangs back and cuts it through covers. The batters take three before the fielder cuts it out.
Full length, on the pads. Green defends it out.
Full length, on middle and leg. Green works it to mid on.
Angled in, fuller, into the pads. Green clips it through mid-wicket for one.
Fuller, angled in, around off. Carey blocks it out watchfully.
Quick single! A length ball, outside off. Carey pushes it to point for one.
Flighted, full, on off. Carey defend it on the front foot.
Flatter, outside off. Carey slashes it to point.
Fuller, around middle and leg. Carey pushes it to mid off for a single.
Fuller, outside off. Green leans in and drives it into covers.
Tossed up, on middle and leg. Green works it towards short mid on.
Length, on middle and leg. Green defends it watchfully.
Fuller, outside off. Alex Carey reverse-sweeps it to point. Straight to the fielder.
A single now. Floated, full and outside off. Alex Carey picks it up nicely and sweeps it to deep square leg for a single.
Fuller, on off. Green eases it to mid off.
Looped up, full, on leg. Green defends it into the deck.
Angled into the pads, Green eases it to mid on.
SIX! BANG! What a strike! Good use of the feet by Green. Tossed up, full, on off. Green dances down the track and smokes it over the bowler's head for a biggie. He moves to 23.
On a length, outside off. Carey pushes it to cover.
Fuller, angled in on off. Alex Carey defends it to the right of the bowler.
Alex Carey defends this full delivery on the front foot.
Full on the stumps. Alex Carey pushes it to mid off.
Outside off, blocked out.
Darted on the pads. Carey tucks it to mid-wicket.
On off, defended out.
Full, outside off. Green pushes it to cover.
Full toss, outside off. Green slaps it to extra cover.
FOUR! Nice intent shown by Green. Tossed up, on off. Cameron Green dances down the track and drives it down the ground for a boundary.
Length, on off. Green punches it to cover.
Tossed up, outside off. Green works it to cover.
Fuller, on the stumps. Carey defends it solidly.
Tossed up, on middle. Carey prods and blocks it out.
Floated, angled down leg. Carey gets low and paddle-sweeps it to fine leg. They take a couple.
Angled in on the pads. Carey tucks it to short mid-wicket.
Full, on off. Carey defends it out.
Carey prods and defends this full delivery with ease. Another tidy over by Sajid Khan comes to an end.
Full, on leg. Green eases it down the ground for a single.
On off, blocked out watchfully.
Fuller, on off. Carey reverse-sweeps it through point for a brace.

Good running! Floated, full, outside off. Carey sweeps it to fine leg. The batters push hard for two and get two. The fielder from the deep scores a direct-hit at the striker's end which wakes up the crowd but Alex Carey was well inside the crease.
Full, outside off. Carey sweeps it to the left of deep square leg for a single. 400 up for Australia. Alex Carey and Cameron Green seem to have their eye in.
On off, blocked out.
FOUR! Carey gets going now! Full length, on off. Carey drives it through covers. The fielder misfields and the ball races away to the boundary.
Darted on the pads. Carey defends it to the leg side.
Floated, outside off. Carey pushes it out to safety.
Full, on middle and leg. Carey blocks it back to the bowler.
On leg, Carey defends it out to the leg side.
Full, outside off. Carey prods to block it into the deck.
Looped up, angled down leg. Green pads it out.
Way down the leg side. Green leaves it alone.
On off, blocked out.

OUT! TIMBER! Nauman Ali comes out with a ripper. This one pitches outside leg and turns in sharply off the deck. Cameron Green leans in and tries to defend it out but misses. The ball zips past his blade and knocks the off pole. Delight for Pakistan.
Howout: b Nauman Ali

Commentary: Flatter ball, around middle and leg. Mitchell Starc clips it towards mid-wicket for a single.
Loopy ball, fuller around middle. Alex Carey sweeps it towards deep square leg for a single.
Full, on leg. Mitchell Starc flicks it to square leg. That will be TEA ON DAY 2.
Tossed up, outside off. Alex Carey defends it to the off side.
Fuller, on off. Carey defends it out.
Full, on the stumps, Carey prods to block it out.
Four dots in a row! Angled into the pads. Carey tucks it to mid-wicket.
Full, on the stumps. Carey defends it back to the bowler.
On off, Carey yet again defends it back to the bowler.
Afridi starts with a delivery thats tails in. Mitchell Starc digs it out sharply.
Length ball, on the pads. Mitchell Starc flicks it to deep square leg for one.
Full length, on leg. Carey flicks it to mid-wicket.
Full length, on off. Carey works it to mid on.
Shaheen Afridi continues to bowl full, on the pads this time. Carey flicks it to mid-wicket. Straight to the fielder.
Too full, on leg. Alex Carey clips it through square leg for three runs. This is too easy for Alex Carey.
Flatter, around off. Carey defends it to cover.
Fuller, on off. Carey reverse-sweeps straight to the fielder at point.
On the stumps, defended out.
Full length, on off. Carey prods and blocks it out.
Tossed up, on off. Carey remains solid in his defense.
Around off, Carey plays it back to the bowler. A maiden by Sajid Khan.
A length ball, on off. Mitchell Starc blocks it back to the bowler.
A full toss now, angled down leg. Starc misses his flick and gets pinged on his pads. Shaheen Afridi appeals but the umpire shows no interest.
Full length, tailing in on off. Mitchell Starc blocks it out safely.
Four dots in a row! Length ball, on the pads. Starc clips it to mid-wicket.
Length ball, on the fourth stump. Mitchell Starc defends it off the underedge into the deck. The umpire signals a no ball, as the bowler oversteps.
Late reverse swing, on off. But still unable to sneak it under Mitchell Starc's blade. He gets his blade down in time. This might be frustrating Shaheen Afridi now.
Full length, on off. Mitchell Starc eases it to mid on for one.
Tosses it up, fuller, on middle. Mitchell Starc lunges and blocks it out.
Full again, spinning away, outside off. Mitchell Starc stays in his crease and taps it towards cover.
Turning away, around off, fullish ball. Mitchell Starc defends it out off the back foot.
Quicker now, this one comes in with the arm. Mitchell Starc hangs back and looks to flick this but misses and gets hit on his thigh pad.
Flighted delivery, full, on middle. Mitchell Starc leans and defends it out solidly.
Loopy once again, outside off, fuller ball. Mitchell Starc presses forward and blocks it out.
NO BALL! On a length, outside off, shaping away. Alex Carey offers no shot to that. Shaheen Afridi has overstepped here and a no ball is called!
Another length delivery, swinging it away, wide of off. Alex Carey stays in his crease and cuts it toward the diving fielder at point.
Much fuller now, angling in, around middle. Alex Carey miscues his drive towards mid off.
Very full again, angling in on the pads. Alex Carey flicks it towards fine leg for a single.
Shaheen Afridi drops it short now, outside off, at around a141 clicks. Mitchell Starc leans back and leaves it alone.
Pitches it u, swinging it in, on middle. Mitchell Starc drives straight to the fielder at mid off.
Back of a length, jagging back in, outside off, at 145.6 clicks. Mitchell Starc lets that go through to the keeper.
Tad quicker through the air now, fuller ball, outside off. Alex Carey lunges and defends it out.
Tosses this one up, much slower this time, on middle. Alex Carey presents the full face of his bat and blocks it out.
Flatter ball, now, darting it on the pads. Alex Carey works it away towards mid-wicket.
FOUR! Top shot! Perfectly executed! Fuller ball again, around middle. Alex Carey gets low and reverse-sweeps this past point for a cracking boundary.
Quick single! Loopy ball, outside off. Alex Carey presses forward and pushes it towards point and scampers through to the other end.
Slower through the air, loopy delivery, fuller again, on middle. Mitchell Starc blocks it out watchfully.
Flatter ball now, full and on middle. Alex Carey prods and defends it out.
Alex Carey is enjoying playing the reverse-sweep! Fuller ball, around off. Alex Carey gets low and once again reverse-sweeps it towards point. Single taken!
Tad shorter now, turning in, around middle. Mitchell Starc knocks it towards cover-point.
Slower through the air this time, outside off, fullish ball. Mitchell Starc lunges and defends it out.
Tad quicker now, spinning back in around middle. Mitchell Starc stays back and defends it out solidly.
Very full, outside off. Mitchell Starc blocks it off the front foot.
Spinning away, full, around off. Alex Carey leans and blocks it out.
Tosses it up, on middle, fuller ball. Alex Carey defends it out watchfully.
Another tossed up ball, around middle. Alex Carey has defended this off the front foot.
Very full again, loopy delivery, outside off. Alex Carey defends it out.
Darting this on the pads, full in length. Alex Carey flicks it uppishly past mid-wicket for three runs.
Loopy ball, full, on middle. Mitchell Starc pushes it back to the bowler.
Looped up, on off, blocked out watchfully.
Floated, outside off. Carey lunges and defends it.
Fuller, outside off. Alex Carey sweeps it to deep square leg for one.
Darted into the pads, Mitchell Starc flicks it to the leg side.
Full, outside off. Starc drives it to cover.
Tossed up, wide outside off. Starc prods and leaves it alone for the keeper.
Looped up, full on middle and leg. Carey defends it back to the bowler off the front foot.
Floated, outside off. Carey defends it to point.

BEATEN! What a beauty! Length, around off. The ball grips and turns away. Alex Carey is drawn forward, he looks to defend it out but gets beaten on the outside edge. This is the closest Pakistan have come to trouble Alex Carey.
On off, blocked back to the bowler.
Tossed up, on off. Alex Carey pushes it down the ground to long off for one.
Full, outside off. Starc defends it to point.
Looped up, outside off. Carey defends it on the front foot.
Fuller, on off. Carey clips it to mid-wicket.
Full and on off. Carey eases it down the ground to long on for a single.
Tossed up, on off. Starc blocks it back to the bowler.

DROPPED! This was an easy chance. Nauman Ali cannot believe it. It is tossed up, full and outside off. Mitchell Starc prods and ends up chipping it back to the bowler. Nauman Ali gets his hands above his head but fails to gather it. Nauman Ali misses out on this golden opportunity.
On off, blocked out solidly.
Angled in, on middle and leg. Carey lunges to defend it back to the bowler.
Full, on off, this one stays a touch low. Carey blocks it back to the bowler.
SIX! BANG! Alex Carey puts his foot on the gas now and rightly so. Fuller, on middle and leg. Alex Carey clears his front leg and tonks it over the long on fence. He moves to 48.
Tossed up, on off, blocked out.
Fuller, on leg, Carey eases it to long on for a single.
Tossed up, outside off, turning away. Mitchell Starc has no stroke to offer, as Mohammad Rizwan collects it to his left.
FIFTY FOR CAREY! What a knock this has been. Fuller, on off. Carey reverse-sweeps it to backward point for a single. The Austalian pavilion applauses this gritty knock.
Full, outside off. Starc looks to defend it out. It runs past slips off the outside edge. They take two.
On middle and leg. Starc tucks it to mid-wicket.
Tossed up, on the pads Starc flicks it to mid-wicket for one.
Fuller, outside off. Carey sweeps it to deep square leg for a single.
Flatter, around off, turns in off the deck. Mitchell Starc plays all around it. The ball lobs to short leg off the pads. Umpire not interested.
Shorter ball, turning away, outside off. Alex Carey pushes it towards cover off the back foot.
Tosses it up now, fuller, around middle. Alex Carey leans to defend but he does so with the other half of his bat.
Flatter ball now, fuller delivery. Alex Carey leans and blocks it out.
Fullish ball, around off. Alex Carey covers the line and blocks it out.
Flatter ball, outside off. Alex Carey defends it out.
Tosses it up, on middle, full in length. Alex Carey leans and blocks it out. A maiden over by Sajid Khan!
Shorter ball, outside off. Mitchell Starc slashes it towards Hasan Ali at point who fumbles and failed to stop the ball. Three runs taken!
Fuller ball, outside off. Alex Carey gets low and sweeps it towards deep square leg for a single.
Shorter now, spinning back in, outside off. Mitchell Starc stays back and defends it out.
Loopy delivery, full again, on middle. Mitchell Starc prods and blocks it out watchfully.
Another flighted delivery, fuller in length, outside off. Mitchell Starc blocks it out solidly.
Spinning in, around middle. Mitchell Starc blocks it out.
Flighted delivery, outside off. Alex Carey defends it out.
Tosses it up again, fullish ball, around off. Alex Carey blocks it, but the ball catches the inside edge and goes towards the leg side.
Tad shorter now, around middle. Alex Carey defends it out off the back foot.
Fuller ball, around off, loopy delivery. Alex Carey reverse-sweeps this towards point. Mitchell Starc wanted a single there, but Alex Carey sends him back.
Flatter ball now, fuller ball, around off. Alex Carey drives it towards mid off.
Much quicker this time, firing it around the off pole, fuller ball. Alex Carey blocks it out.
FOUR! Top shot! Hasan Ali serves a fuller ball, angling in around middle. Mitchell Starc flicks it uppishly over mid on for a boundary.
Full again, on middle. Mitchell Starc pushes it back to the bowler.
Pitches it up, outside off. Mitchell Starc drives straight to the fielder at mid off.
Change of angle now! Hasan Ali goes 'round the wicket, serves a shorter ball, on middle. Mitchell Starc pulls and finds the fielder at deep square leg. Single taken!
Back of a length, outside off. Alex Carey stands tall and blocks it out.
Fuller now, outside off. Alex Carey drives to the fielder at mid off.
Shaheen Afridi delivers a fuller ball, down the leg side. Mitchell Starc looks to flick but misses.
Angling in, on middle, fuller ball. Mitchell Starc drives it towards mid on.
Leg bye! Swinging back in, on the pads, on a length. Mitchell Starc misses his flick and gets rapped on his pad. The ball rolls towards fine leg and the batters steal a leg bye!
Fuller ball, around middle. Alex Carey defends it towards mid on.

FOUR! Classy! Shaheen Afridi overpitches this delivery, around middle, at around 135 clicks. Alex Carey presents the full face of the bat and drives it straight down the ground. The fielder from mid on chases it but the ball wins the race. A boundary! 450 up for Australia!

FOUR! Back-to-back boundaries! Another glorious drive! Shaheen Afridi pitches it up once again, outside off. Alex Carey leans and drives it past extra cover for a gorgeous boundary. That brings up the 50-run stand between these two!
Full length, outside off. Starc drives it to mid off.
Back of a length, outside off. Starc defends it out to cover.
Swing and a miss! Full length, outside off. Starc looks to heave it away but misses.
NO BALL! A sharp bouncer, on middle Mitchell Starc ducks under it. The umpire signals a no ball, as Ali oversteps.
Length ball, on off. Starc hangs back and defends it to cover.
Good length, around leg, angled across the left-hander. Mitchell Starc blocks it back to the bowler.
Touch short, on the pads. Starc tucks it off his hips to the leg side.
Back of a length, outside off. Carey leaves it alone.
Short ball, on off, blocked out solidly.
A short ball, again, on the body this time. Carey pulls it to fine leg for a single.
Back of a length, sliding down leg. Mitchell Starc swings wildly but does not connect.
Back of a length, outside off. Starc lets it be. This one dies till it reaches the keeper.
Length, on off. Starc blocks it out.
Length ball, on off. Carey pushes it out.
Good length, on off. Carey works it to mid off.
Full length, on off. Carey gets his blade down in time to dig it out.
Length ball, on off. Carey gets it over the bowler on a bounce. The batters take a single.
FOUR! Easy pickings. Short ball, on the bodyline. Mitchell Starc pulls it to fine leg for a boundary.
Good length, on off. Starc defends it to the leg side.
A single now, as Carey drives it down the ground.
Full, on off. Starc prods and blocks it back to the bowler.
Full, on middle and leg. Starc tucks it to the leg side.
Fuller, on the pads. Starc flicks it through mid-wicket for a single.
On off, blocked out solidly.
Fuller, on off, Carey defends it out watchfully.
Fuller ball, turning in on middle. Mitchell Starc defends it out.
Tad shorter, spinning back in, outside off. Mitchell Starc hangs back and pushes it towards cover.
Fuller ball, turning in, around off. Mitchell Starc leans forward but misses and gets pinged on the pads.
Beaten this time! Another fuller ball, quicker through the air, outside off. Mitchell Starc prods to drive but misses.
Swing and a miss! Another fuller ball, outside off. Mitchell Starc once again lunges and looks to drive but once again, he fails to get any bat on it.
Tad shorter now, spinning back in, around off. Mitchell Starc hangs back and pushes it towards cover.
Tad quicker, full, on middle. Alex Carey leans and blocks it out.
Fuller ball, loopy delivery, outside off, turning away. Alex Carey prods and defends it out solidly.
Tosses it up again, full, outside off. Alex Carey lunges and pushes it towards cover.
Shorter ball, on the pads. Alex Carey flicks it past square leg for a brace.

DROPPED AND FOUR! A fuller ball, around middle. Alex Carey waits for it and miscues his heaves towards mid on. Hasan Ali leaps to his right, but the ball brushes off his hands and goes towards long on for a boundary.
Shorter ball, outside off. Alex Carey pushes it towards cover. Single taken!
Fuller ball, on middle. Alex Carey pushes it uppishly towards mid-wicket for a single.
Fuller ball, around off. Mitchell Starc slices it past point for a brace.
Fuller ball, around the fifth stump line. Mitchell Starc hangs back and defends it out.
Tosses it up, full, on middle. Mitchell Starc leans and defends this one.
Loopy ball, again, fuller delivery. Mitchell Starc defends this one off the front foot.
Quicker now, outside off. Starc blocks this one off the back foot.
Fuller now, outside off. Alex Carey pushes it towards cover.
Quicker now, very full, on the pads. Alex Carey whips it towards deep mid-wicket for a brace.
Full now, around middle and off. Alex Carey defends it out solidly.
SIX! Bang! What a shot by Alex Carey! A fuller ball, around middle. Alex Carey clears his front foot and tonks it over long on for a biggie!
Loopy ball, full, on middle. Alex Carey lunges and blocks it out.
Pitches it up again, on middle. Alex Carey pushes it towards mid-wicket.
Tad shorter, outside the off pole. Mitchell Starc pushes it towards mid off.
Outside off, slower through the air. Mitchell Starc leaves it alone.
Tad shorter now, around teh fifth stump line. Mitchell Starc punches it to the fielder at mid off.
Fuller ball now, on middle. Mitchell Starc knocks it down to long on and rotates the strike!
Full again, on middle. Alex Carey sweeps it towards deep square leg for a single. He moves to 80 with that!
Loopy ball, outside off, full in length. Mitchell Starc looks to defend this, but the ball goes off the inside edge towards mid-wicket.
Full, on off. Carey defends it to cover.
Full length, outside off. Alex Carey drives it along the ground towards sweeper cover for a brace.
A single as this is worked through covers.
Floated, full, on off. Starc defends it back to the bowler.
Tossed up, on off. Starc defends it into the deck.
Quicker, fuller, on middle and leg. Mitchell Starc goes back and defends it out.
Tossed up, outside off. Alex Carey picks it up nicely and paddles it to fine leg for a brace.
FOUR! Beats the man at leg slip and bags a boundary. This is full, angled down leg. Alex Carey drags his sweep to fine leg for a boundary. He moves to 89.
Looped up, around off. Alex Carey tries to reverse sweep but gets beaten by the turn.
Fuller, on middle and leg. Alex Carey steps across and sweeps it to deep square leg for one. Into the 90s now.
Short and outside off. Starc cuts it hard but straight to the fielder. Misses out this time.
Full outside off. Starc procs and blocks it out.
On off, blocked out.
Full and on off. Carey reverse-sweeps it through backward point for a couple.
On off, blocked out solidly.
Fuller, outside off. Carey sweeps it through square leg for a single.
Full, on off, pushed to cover.
500 up for Australia. Tossed up, on off. Starc hits it past the bowler and gets a single to mid on. These two have batted brilliantly for the visitors. An applause from the pavilion as well.
Full, on off. Starc pushes it to extra cover.
Angled in, full, on off. Mitchell Starc defends it to point.
Length, outside off. Starc pushes it to cover.
Slower through the air, down leg. Starc glances it down to fine leg for a couple.
Short ball, outside off. Starc cuts it through point for a single.

OUT! TIMBER! Heartbreak for Carey. Babar Azam the part time spinner sends back Alex Carey on 93. Just two more overs left in the day and Alex Carey holes out. It is full, slower through the air, on off. Alex Carey gets low and tries to sweep it away but misses. One of the rare moments in thing innings of Carey. He has middled atleast 90% of his shot and this miss has cost him his maiden Test century.
Howout: b Babar Azam

Commentary: On leg, flicked to mid-wicket for a single.
Full and on the stumps. Cummins defends it to short leg.
Floated, full, on off. Cummins defends it out.
Outside off, Cummins eases it to point.
Full, on off. Cummins defends it out.
Fuller, outside off. Cummins blocks it of the front foot.
Flighted, full, on middle. Starc bunts it to mid on for one.
On middle and leg. Cummins stays back and blocks out.
Flatter, on off, Cummins defends it to cover.
On off, blocked out watchfully.
Fuller, on leg. Cummins blocks it to short leg.
It is a full delivery, outside off, turning in late. Pat Cummins leaves it alone for the keeper. THAT WILL BE STUMPS ON DAY 2.
Shaheen Afridi starts with a good-length ball, right on top of off. Mitchell Starc gets behind the line and blocks it back to the bowler.

OUT! TAKEN! Shaheen Afridi doesn't waste any time and strikes in his first over of Day 3! Bowls a good-length ball, outside off this time. Offers some width and Mitchell Starc leans onto it and tries to go over covers. Doesn't time it that well and Azhar Ali at covers takes a simple catch.
Howout: c Azhar Ali b Shaheen Afridi

Commentary: Length ball from 'round the wicket, on middle, angling in. Mitchell Swepson does well to defend it out.

TWO LEG BYES! Full and down leg, Mitchell Swepson misses his glance. The ball brushes his pads and rolls to fine leg. The fielder in the deep does well to stop the ball with his leg. The batters take two.
Length ball, outside off. Mitchell Swepson drives it towards covers.

FOUR! First runs off the bat for Mitchell Swepson! Opens his account in Test cricket with a boundary. A full toss from Afridi, outside off. Mitchell Swepson accepts the gift and slices it behind point and the ball races away to the fence.
Full and on the pads, Pat Cummins eases it down to long on for a run.
Quick and full, on middle. Mitchell Swepson pushes it to mid on.
Drifting on the pads, Mitchell Swepson nudges it to mid-wicket.
Floats it up, on middle. Mitchell Swepson drives it straight down the pitch.
Tosses it up, on off. Swepson pushes it to the off side.
Flatter ball, on off. Swepson blocks it out off the front foot.
FOUR! Length ball, on off. Pat Cummins stays back and guides it to third man. Went off the edge but still will get a boundary.
Full and angling into middle and leg, Cummins comes forward with a straight bat to pat it solidly into the leg side.
Short ball, on middle. Pat Cummins mistimes his pull to the leg side.
Full and on off, at 140.7 kph. Pat Cummins knocks it towards covers.
Touch fuller, on off. Cummins pushes it to point for a quick single.
A full toss, on the pads. Mitchell Swepson flicks it to deeps square leg for a single. He keeps the strike.
Tossed up, outside off, slower through the air. Mitchell Swepson taps it on the off side.
Loopy ball, on off. Swepson pats it back to the bowler.
Flatter, outside off. Mitchell Swepson steers it past point for a run.
Floats it up, around off. Pat Cummins strides forward and blocks.
SIX! Up and over! Full and on off, in the slot. Pat Cummins gets under it and slogs it over long on for a maximum. Looks like Australia want to get 550 on the board.
Flatter ball, on middle and leg. Cummins nudges it to mid-wicket for a quick single.
Loopy ball, on middle. Cummins blocks it out.
Full and on off, Cummins stays back and works it to mid-wicket.
Flatter ball, on middle. Pushed back to the bowler.
Full and on off, Cummins prods and pushes it to long on. He rotates the strike.
Tosses it up, on middle, turning in. Mitchell Swepson does well to block it off the back foot.
Slightly full, spinning into the batter. Mitchell Swepson squeezes it back to the bowler.
Fuller delivery, around middle. Pat Cummins knocks it down to long on and rotates the strike.
Tad quicker, on the pads. Mitchell Swepson stays back and flicks it past square leg for a brace.
Fuller again, around middle and off. Mitchell Swepson blocks it out.
Pitches it up again, around middle, tad quicker. Mitchell Swepson defends it out off the back foot.
Fuller ball, quick, spinning away, around off. Mitchell Swepson cuts it late towards point for a single.
SIX! HIGH AND HANDSOME! Tosses it up, fuller ball, around middle. Pat Cummins gets low and heaves it over deep mid-wicket for another biggie.
Fuller ball, spinning in a tad, outside off. Mitchell Swepson defends it out off the back foot.
Fuller ball, around middle. Mitchell Swepson knocks it with the inner half of his bat towards mid on for a single.
Loopy ball, full, around middle. Pat Cummins pushes it towards mid off.
Flatter ball, around middle. Pat Cummins flicks it towards mid-wicket.
Turning in, tad shorter, around middle. Pat Cummins stays back and clips it towards square leg.
Tad shorter, around middle. Pat Cummins knocks it to long on for a single.
Hasan Ali begins with a length ball, outside off. Pat Cummins guides it towards third man for a single.
Another good-length delivery, outside off. Mitchell Swepson pushes it towards cover with the bottom half of the bat as the ball stayed low.
Back of a length, outside off. Mitchell Swepson punches it off the back foot past cover-point for a brace.
Another short ball, around middle. Mitchell Swepson swivels and pulls it towards fine leg for a single.
Shorter again, around off. Pat Cummins tries to cut this but he is cramped for room, the ball deflects off his gloves and lands short of the slip fielder.
On a length, around middle. Pat Cummins flicks it towards square leg.
Tosses it up, around middle, fuller ball. Mitchell Swepson drags it with the inner half of his bat towards mid-wicket for one.
Quicker now, firing it on middle and leg. Pat Cummins defends it out.
FOUR! Top shot! Another loopy balll, full, around middle. Pat Cummins gets down on his knee and sweeps it between deep mid-wicket and deep square leg for a boundary.
Loopy ball again, full, around off. Pat Cummins sweeps it towards mid-wicket for a single.
Flighted ball, outside off. Mitchell Swepson Swepson drags it off the inner half to the leg side for a single.

SIX! Tossed up, on middle and leg. Pat Cummins picks the bones of that one and slog-sweeps it over deep mid-wicket for a maximum. And with that, enough is enough says Pat Cummins! An unbeaten 51-run stand between these two and Australia have declared at 556/9.
Mitchell Starc begins with a length ball, angling in, around middle. Abdullah Shafique stays back and taps it with the outer half of his bat towards cover.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Abdullah Shafique leans and defends it out solidly.

Bye! Fuller ball, down the leg side. Abdullah Shafique looks to flick but misses. Alex Carey dives to his left, stretches his left hand out to grab the ball, but fails to do so. The batters sneak in a run. Good stop though! Replay shows that it went off the pads but the umpire has given it as byes.
Back of a length, shaping away, outside off. Imam-ul-Haq leaves it alone.
Another shorter ball, shaping away, wide of off, at 145.5 clicks. Imam-ul-Haq watches it sail through to the keeper.
On a length, shaping away, around off. Imam-ul-Haq defends it out off the front foot.
Pat Cummins begins with a shortish delivery, angling in, around off, at around 131 clicks. Abdullah Shafique blocks it out solidly.
On a length now, outside off, at 135 clicks. Abdullah Shafique presses forward and defends it out.

Almost chopped on! Good-length delivery, around the fourth stump line, at 135.1 clicks. Abdullah Shafique hangs back looks to defend but the ball goes off the toe-end of the bat and just misses the off pole before going to the keeper. That one kept low as well!
Fuller now, around middle. Abdullah Shafique defends it towards square leg.
Fraction shorter now, around middle, at around 132 clicks. Abdullah Shafique pushes it towards mid-wicket.
On a length, around off. Abdullah Shafique presses forward to defend but he does so with the inner half of his bat. A maiden for Pat Cummins!
Length ball, down the leg side. Imam-ul-Haq lets that go through to the keeper.
Much fuller now, angling in around middle. Imam-ul-Haq pushes it towards mid on.
Outside off this time, tad fuller. Imam-ul-Haq closes the face of his bat and taps it towards mid-wicket.
Back of a length, outside off, at 143.1 clicks. Imam-ul-Haq leans back and leaves it alone.
FOUR! Imam-ul-Haq gets off the mark in style! Mitchell Starc serves a fuller delivery, on the pads. Imam-ul-Haq uses his wrists and flicks it past mid-wicket for a boundary.
Shorter ball, outside off. Imam-ul-Haq defends it out solidly.
Angling in, tad fuller, angling in around middle. Abdullah Shafique lunges and defends it out.
Full once again, around middle and leg. Abdullah Shafique flicks it towards mid-wicket for a single. Abdullah Shafique opens his account with that!
Well bowled! Length ball, shaping away, outside off. Imam-ul-Haq stays in his crease and looks to block this but he beaten on the outside edge.
On a length again, shaping away, wide of off. Imam-ul-Haq shoulders his arms to that.

FOUR! Edgy runs! Tad fuller now, outside off. Imam-ul-Haq leans and looks to defend this, but the ball goes off the outside edge between second slip and gully all the way towards the fence for a boundary!
Outside off, on a length. Imam-ul-Haq leaves it alone.
Back of a length, outside off. Abdullah Shafique taps it towards point for a single.

Much fuller now, on middle. Imam-ul-Haq pushes it back to the bowler. Starc collects the ball and flicks it back to the stumps, the ball goes on and hits Imam-ul-Haq on the pads. Australian puts in a friendly appeal there!
Tad shorter again, around off. Imam-ul-Haq defends it out off the back foot.
Good-length delivery, around middle, at around 143 clicks. Imam-ul-Haq taps it towards mid-wicket.
Short ball now, around middle. Imam-ul-Haq ducks underneath it.
Shaping away, outside off, on a length. Imam-ul-Haq offers no shot to that.
Good-lengtth ball, sliding down leg. Abdullah Shafique misses his flick.
Length ball, angling in on middle and leg. Abdullah Shafique clips it to deep square leg for a single.
Good-length ball, angling across the left-hander, Imam-ul-Haq lifts his bat and lets it go.
Length ball, lands comfortable outside off. Imam-ul-Haq shoulders arms.
Full and shaping across, around off. Imam-ul-Haq brings his bat down and it goes off the outside edge past gully for a couple of runs. The line is perfect there for Cummins!

Peach! So so agonizingly close there! Good length and slants it right across the off stump corridor, Imam-ul-Haq plays down the original line and looks to defend. The ball whistles past the edge by a whisker!
Good length, on middle. Abdullah Shafique strides forward and works it on the leg side for a single.
Full and down the leg side. Imam-ul-Haq looks to flick but misses.
Fuller in length, outside off. Imam-ul-Haq covers the line and defends it towards covers.
On a length, on off. Imam-ul-Haq dabs it to backward point for a single.
On a length, on middle. the ball straightens up after pitching. Abdullah Shafique blocks it right under his eyes.
Outside off, on a length. Abdullah Shafique allows it to go through.
Starts with a full ball, outside off. Imam-ul-Haq presses forward and defends it off the front foot.
Drifting on leg, Imam-ul-Haq blocks it out.
Tosses it up, on off. Imam-ul-Haq stays back and defends it back to the bowler.
Loopy ball, on middle and leg. Imam-ul-Haq plays it to mid-wicket.
Flatter, on middle. Imam-ul-Haq knocks it back to the bowler.
A maiden for Lyon! Floats it up, on middle. Imam-ul-Haq keeps it out.
Short of a length, on middle. Abdullah Shafique misses his tuck. Gets struck on the pads.

FOUR! Lovely shot! Full and angling in on leg, Abdullah Shafique clears his front leg and drives it to long on. Wonderful strike from Abdullah Shafique! Superb timing on that one and there's no stopping that. A boundary!
On a length, on off. Abdullah Shafique presses forward and defends.
Back of a length, around off. Abdullah Shafique gets behind the line and blocks it from the crease.
Touch fuller, outside off. Abdullah Shafique pushes it towards point for a single.

That's a shocker of a leave from Imam-ul-Haq but the angle might have saved him here! Good-length ball, angling across, on off. Imam-ul-Haq shoulders arms to that one and the ball hits him on the pads. Australia appeal for an lbw but the umpire says no. They don't opt for the review as well.
Tossed up, on off. Abdullah Shafique strides forward and blocks it out.
Full and on middle, Abdullah Shafique is solid in his defence.
On off, Abdullah Shafique eases it down to long on for a run.
Floats it up, on middle. Imam-ul-Haq advances down the track and looks to defend but gets hit on the pads first. Mild appeal for an lbw there.
Full and quick, on off. Imam-ul-Haq gets forward and defends it with soft hands.
Flatter delivery, outside off. Imam-ul-Haq defends it solidly off the front foot.
Pat Cummins drops it short now, around middle. Abdullah Shafique ducks underneath it.
On a length, outside off, at 141 clicks. Abdullah Shafique pushes it towards cover off the back foot.
Shaping away, outside off, on a length. Abdullah Shafique taps it past point and takes a single.
Outside off, swinging away, on a length. Imam-ul-Haq leaves it alone.
Tad fuller now, down the leg side this time. Imam-ul-Haq looks to flick but misses.
Good-length delivery, angling away, around off. Imam-ul-Haq blocks it out watchfully towards mid off.
Fuller ball, turning it in, outside off. Abdullah Shafique presses forward and defends it out.
Sharp turn this time! This one lands on a fuller length, wide off off, and turns in. Abdullah Shafique lunges forward and leaves it alone.
Tad fuller, around off. Abdullah Shafique defends it out.
Quicker through the air, touch fuller again, around off. Abdullah Shafique lunges and defends it out.
Fuller ball, drifting in around middle. Abdullah Shafique leans and tucks it towards mid-wicket for a single.
Quicker again, at around 91 clicks, fuller ball, around middle. Imam-ul-Haq leans and blocks it towards mid-wicket.
Mitchell Swepson begins with a fuller ball, down the leg side. Abdullah Shafique taps is towards square leg.
Fuller ball, spinning away, around off. Abdullah Shafique knocks it to long off for a single.
Tad shorter, spinning in, around middle. Imam-ul-Haq tucks it towards square leg.
Loopy delivery, full and outside off. Imam-ul-Haq leans and defends it out towards cover.

Direct hit.. but Imam-ul-Haq is safe! A fuller ball, outside off. Imam-ul-Haq pushed it towards mid off and scampers through to the other end. Pat Cummins throws it directly at the stumps at the non-striker's end.
Fuller ball, around middle. Abdullah Shafique taps it towards mid-wicket.
Fuller ball, around middle, tad quicker. Imam-ul-Haq steps down and pushes it back to the bowler.

OUT! RUN OUT! Australia have their early breakthrough! There was never a single there! Mitchell Swepson with a brilliant throw! He may not have got a wicket in his first over, but he helps Australia provide their first wicket! A fuller ball, spinning away, around the pads. Imam-ul-Haq leans to defend, but the goes off the outside edge towards short third man. Imam-ul-Haq looks at Abdullah Shafique who has left his crease for a single and he too leaves his crease. Mitchell Swepson runs to his right, grabs the ball with his right hand, and throws it directly on the stumps at the keeper's end. The replay shows that Abdullah Shafique is no where near the crease and he has to walk back!
Howout: run out (Mitchell Swepson)

Commentary: Very full, on off. Azhar Ali leans forward and drives it to mid off. Nathan Lyon is aiming for the rough.
Quicker, outside off. Azhar Ali strides forward and defends it towards covers.
Lyon hits the rough and tosses it up, on off. Ali hangs back and defends.
Flatter ball, Azhar Ali rocks back and keeps it out.
FOUR! Loopy ball, on off. Imam-ul-Haq steps out and smacks it straight down the ground. Good intent from Imam-ul-Haq and gets a boundary.
Full and on middle, Imam-ul-Haq lunges forward and defends.
Short and on off, Imam-ul-Haq stays back and plays it to mid-wicket for a single.
Quicker deliver, on middle. Azhar Ali blocks it out off the front foot.
Drifing it on the pads. Ali tucks it to fine leg for a run.
Sharp turn! Comes in from outside off and Imam-ul-Haq nicely punches it to mid on for a run.
Floats it up, on off. Imam-ul-Haq hangs back and defends.
A slider, on off. Imam-ul-Haq uses his feet to get to the pitch of the ball and blocks it out.
Quick again, on off. Imam-ul-Haq keeps it out off the back foot.
Flatter and quicker, around off. Imam-ul-Haq stays solid in defence.
On off, blocked out.
Tosses it up, spinning away, on off. Imam-ul-Haq leans forward and defends. A maiden!
Short and quick, on off. Azhar Ali goes back and nudges it to deep mid-wicket for a single.
A juicy full toss, on off. Imam-ul-Haq drives it well but finds the cover fielder.
Tosses it up, outside off. Imam-ul-Haq guides it towards cover for a single.
Spinning away from outside off, Azhar Ali presses forward and looks to push. The ball goes off the outside edge to point.
Drags the length back and bowls it short, on middle, the ball stays low. Azhar Ali tucks it to mid-wicket for one.
Flighted delivery, outside off. Imam-ul-Haq leans forward and defends.
Full and fired into the rough. Azhar Ali lunges forward and pokes it to the off side.
Quick and full, outside off. Azhar Ali wrists it to mid on.
Tosses it up, on off, into the rough. Azhar Ali meets it with a dead bat.
Quicker, around off. Azhar Ali works it to mid on.
Azhar Ali stays back to this loopy ball and defends.
Full and outside off. Azhar Ali is solid in his defence.
Flighted delivery, on off. Imam-ul-Haq steps out and works it to deep square leg for a single.
Full and on middle, Azhar Ali clears his front leg and works it to mid on.
On the pads, pushed gently to mid on for a single this time.
Flighted ball, around off. Imam-ul-Haq defends it out.
Imam-ul-Haq steps out to the pitch of this quick one outside off, into the rough but Imam pokes right under his eyeline.
Very full, outside off. Imam-ul-Haq steps out again and flicks it to mid-wicket. THAT WILL BE LUNCH ON DAY 3!
A fuller ball, this one lands on the rough area around off, and turns back in a tad. Azhar Ali leans and defends it out.
SIX! BANG! Some aggression shown by Azhar Ali! Fuller ball again, around off. Azhar Ali shimmies down the pitch and tonks it over long off for a biggie!
Flatter ball, tad quicker, around middle. Azhar Ali knocks it to long on for a single.
Shorter now, around middle and leg. Imam-ul-Haq hangs back and tucks it towards square leg for a single.
Quicker now, fuller ball, around middle. Imam-ul-Haq leans and defends it out.

OUT! CAUGHT! Oh, dear! Pakistan are throwing it away here! This was an unnecessary shot by Imam-ul-Haq! Nathan Lyon tosses it up just a tad, fuller ball, around middle. Imam-ul-Haq dances down the track and tries to heave it over mid on, but he does so with the inner half of his bat. The ball lobs up and goes to Pat Cummins at mid on, who hops a bit and pouches the ball near his head. Pakistan have lost both their openers now!
Howout: c Pat Cummins b Nathan Lyon

Commentary: Length ball, outside off. Azhar Ali dabs it to deep point and crosses ends.
On a good length, on off. Babar Azam shows full face of the bat and blocks it out.
Fuller in length, on off, a bit of an inward movement. Babar Azam jams it back to the bowler.
Length ball, on off, Babar Azam plays it towards covers.

NOT OUT! Cummins hurls an inswinging ball, on middle, on a full length. Babar Azam with no feet movement looks to flick but misses and gets hit on the front pad. Huge shout from Australia for an lbw but Aleem Dar shakes his head. Pat Cummins opts to challenge the umpire and signals 'T'. UltraEdge shows that the ball was very close to bat and pad. The third umpire reckons that it hit bat and pad at the same time and asks the on-field umpire to stay with the decision. So Babar Azam survives. Marnus Labuschagne certainly thought they have got Babar Azam and was all smiles but now is not happy with the decision.
Fuller ball, angling in around middle. Babar Azam flicks it towards fine leg for a brace.
Fullish delivery, angling in around middle. Azhar Ali taps it towards mid-wicket for a single.
On a length ball, coming back in, around the pads. Babar Azam tucks it towards square leg for a single.
Back of a length, on off. Azhar Ali rides the bounce and taps it towards point.
Fine delivery! A yorker, outside off. Azhar Ali keeps it out by steering it to the off side.
Comes 'round the wicket now and bowls a length ball, on middle. Azhar Ali works it to deep square leg for a single.
Fuller in length, on off. Azam blocks it out.
Length ball, on middle and leg. Azhar Ali defends it on the leg side off the back foot.
On a length, on off. Azhar Ali pushes it to cover-point.
Short of a length, on off. Azhar Ali taps it to point.
Outside off, Ali gets forward and steers it to point.
Back of a length, outside off. Azhar Ali lets it be.
Full and outside off, Azhar Ali lets it sail through to the keeper. A maiden!
A yorker, on off. Babar Azam squeezes it back to the bowler.
Length ball, well outside off. Babar Azam watches it and lets it go.
Full again, outside off, at 143 kph. Babar Azam drives it towards covers. The fielder there does well to stop the ball sliding to his left.
Back of a length, on leg. Babar Azam tucks it to deep square leg for a single.
Full and outside off, tailing a tad away. Azhar Ali goes chasing after it but gets beaten on the outside edge.
Terrific bowling! Right on the money, a yorker, on middle, at 142 clicks. Azhar Ali gets behind the ball and keeps it out.
Short of a length, on middle. Azam prods and glances it to square leg.
Length ball, nipping back in, on off. Pushed to mid on.

FOUR! My goodness, how good is that? Short of a length from Cummins, just outside off. Babar Azam stands tall, watches the ball closely, and punches it through covers. Impeccable timing and he holds the pose for the cameras as well. The ball just races away to the fence. Beauty of a shot and rightly deserved a boundary.
On middle and leg, kept low. Babar Azam blocks it out.
Full, on off. Azam mistimes his drive to mid off.
Length ball, keeps low, on off. Babar Azam covers the line and keeps it out.
Another yorker from Starc outside off, Ali digs it out to the off side off the front foot.

FOUR BYES! Poor from Starc this time. Bangs a bouncer on leg, went further away with the swing. Azhar Ali ducks under it and there is nothing Alex Carey could do about it. He dives full stretch to his left but the ball was still not in reach. It races away to the fine leg fence.
Short of a length, outside off. Azhar Ali defends it from the crease.

OUT! TAKEN! Pakistan lose another wicket. The plan has worked for Mitchell Starc and Australia! Starc goes back to bowling full and outside off, inviting the batter to drive. Azhar Ali does go after it. He got beaten a couple of times but this time he perishes. Goes chasing after a wide ball and invites a thick outside edge. The ball flies to Cameron Green at second slip and he takes a good sharp catch. Pakistan are in a spot of bother now! They have lost their top three batters.
Howout: c Cameron Green b Mitchell Starc

Commentary: OUT! LBW! This is Mitchell Starc at his best! Comes over the wicket for the southpaw and bowls a sensational toe-crushing yorker, on middle, with a hint of inward movement. Fawad Alam has an unusual stance and he finds it tough to jam it out. He tries to block but misses and gets thudded on the pads. A huge shout from Australia and the umpire agrees and shows his dreaded finger. Fawad Alam does opt for a review after having a chat with Babar Azam. UltraEgde shows nothing and Ball Tracking shows three reds. Fawad Alam walks back for a golden duck and Mitchell Starc is on a hat-trick now. Australia are all over Pakistan at the moment.
Howout: lbw b Mitchell Starc

Commentary: Rizwan just about survies the hat-trick ball. Starc with a good-length delivery from 'round the wicket, on off, shaping away. Mohammad Rizwan goes behind the line and tries to defend but gets beaten by the swing. The ball whizzes past the outside edge. A top over from Mitchell Starc.
Short of a length, outside off. Babar Azam punches it through covers. There is a sweeper cover for protection and the batters run two.
On a length, on middle. Babar Azam defends it out.

FOUR! This time Babar Azam will get a boundary! Short of a length, outside off. Babar Azam rides the bounce and slaps it through mid off to bag a boundary. He is going to play his shots and not allow the pressure to come onto him.
Good-length ball, outside off. Azam plays it to mid on.
Length ball, outside off. Azam shoulders arms.
On a length, outside off, swinging away. Babar Azam taps it to the off side.
NO BALL! On a length, outside off. Mohammad Rizwan keeps it out. Mitchell Starc will have to reload again as he has overstepped.
Fuller in length, outside off. Mohammad Rizwan drives it to wide of mid off.
Fuller, angling in, on the pads. Mohammad Rizwan works it to mid-wicket.
Full again, outside off, Rizwan drives it to mid off for a run.

Another full ball, outside off. Babar Azam crouches and drives it to cover. Good fielding by the fielder there as he dives to his left and stops it one-handed. Scores a direct hit at the bowler's end as well but Mohammad Rizwan was well in.
Back of a length, angling in at 140 clicks, Babar Azam stands tall to defend it right under his eyelines.
Length ball, on leg. Babar Azam tries to tuck it on the leg side. The ball goes off the outside edge and races away to deep point before the fielder cuts it off. Gets two runs!
Clipped! Drifting on the pads and Mohammad Rizwan clips it through mid-wicket. Good timing on that one and gets three runs for it.
Short ball, outside off. Babar Azam sways away from the line.
NO BALL! Good length, on middle. Babar Azam covers the line and keeps it out. Green oversteps and will have to reload.
Back of a length, on middle. Babar Azam stands tall and defends.
On off, kept out.
Back of a length, on off. Azam gets right behind it to block.
Babar Azam closes the bat-face and clips this in front of mid-wicket.
Back of a length, on off. Mohammad Rizwan stands on his toes and knocks it back to the bowler.
Touch fuller, outside off. Mohammad Rizwan gets forward and defends it towards covers.

DROPPED! Good-length ball, outside off, shaping away a little bit. Mohammad Rizwan looks to defend but gets an outside edge. Alex Carey dives to his right and Steven Smith at first slip dives to his left. He gets his hands on it but couldn't grab it. It goes to third man for a brace. Had Steven Smith left it for the keeper to collect, Australia might have got another wicket.

NOT OUT! Length ball, outside off. Mohammad Rizwan gets behind the line but shoulders arms. He gets pinned on the pads and Australia appeal for an lbw. The umpire raises his finger as well. Pakistan immediately take a review. Ball Tracking shows that the ball is missing the wickets by quite some distance. The batter was a yard out outside off, not sure why the on-field umpire gave it out. The on-field decison is overturned and rightly so. Pakistan retain their review as well.
Overpitched delivery, on off. Mohammad Rizwan drives it back to the bowler. Pat Cummins has a shy at the striker's end but Mohammad Rizwan was well in.
Length, on off. Mohammad Rizwan looks to defend but gets an inside edge onto the pads.
On a length, angling in around middle. Babar Azam stays in his crease and defends it out.
Good-length delivery, tailing back in, around middle and off, at 137.5 clicks. Babar Azam blocks it out.
Another delivery swinging in, tad shorter this time, around off. Babar Azam presents the full face of the bat and defends it out.
Now an outswinger, on a fuller length, outside off. at 138.9 clicks. Babar Azam lunges and pushes it back to the bowler.
Pitches it up again, around the fifth stum line. Babar Azam defends it towards cover.
Shaping back in now, on a shortish length, outside off. Babar Azam defends it out.

OUT! CAUGHT BEHIND! Pat Cummins strikes this time, and gets rid of Mohammad Rizwan! Another one bites the dust! Pakistan continues to tumble! What a peach of a delivery, he was trying this earlier on as well, but he gets him this time! On a good length, outside off, shaping away just a tad. Mohammad Rizwan leans and looks to defend this but the ball goes off the outside edge towards the keeper. Alex Carey takes an easy catch to dismiss Mohammad Rizwan. Pakistan have lost half their side now!
Howout: c Alex Carey b Pat Cummins

Commentary: On a length, around middle and off. Faheem Ashraf pushes it towards mid on.
Outside off, tad shorter, shaping away. Faheem Ashraf leaves it alone!

FOUR! Faheem Ashraf opens his account in some fine fashion! Touch fuller now, angling in, around middle and leg. Faheem Ashraf flicks it uppishly away from square leg towards the fence for a boundary.
Fuller in length again, around middle. Faheem Ashraf defends it out.

Pat Cummins comes 'round the wicket now, serves a shortish ball, outside off. Faheem Ashraf was in two minds, whether to play or leave it, but he keeps the bat hanging and the ball goes off the toe end away from gully. End of a successful over by Pat Cummins!
On a length, around middle and leg. Babar Azam flicks it towards square leg for a single.
In the air...but safe! Fullish ball, outside off. Faheem Ashraf drives it uppishly, towards cover. The ball lobs and lands just short of Marnus Labuschagne there!

OUT! LBW! Another goes back to the hut! Pakistan are in deep trouble here! Cameron Green strikes this time and sends back Faheem Ashraf early. Cameron Green comes 'round the wicket, serves a length ball, angling in around middle and leg. Faheem Ashraf looks to flick this, but he misses as the ball tails back in sharply. He gets rapped on his front pad and the Australian's appeal immediately. The umpire raises his finger. He did consult Babar Azam for review, but he decided against it. Pakistan are all over the place. They lose their sixth wicket.
Howout: lbw b Cameron Green

Commentary: Length ball, shaping back in, around middle. Sajid Khan defends it out.
On a length, outside off again. Sajid Khan leaves it allone. The ball dies out till it reaches the keeper.
Length ball, down leg this time. Sajid Khan leaves it alone.
Fullish delivery, around teh fifth stump line. Babar Azam leans defends it out solidly.
Back of a length this time, around middle. Babar Azam taps it towards square leg for a single.
Beautiful! This one lands on a length and shapes away outside off. Sajid Khan thought this one was coming back in, as he tries to play it inside the line, however, he misses.
Fullish ball, outside off. Sajid Khan pushes it towards cover.
Another beautiful delivery! On a length, around off. Sajid Khan looks to defend but gets beaten.
Much fuller now, around off. Sajid Khan pushes it towards mid off.
Fuller ball, sliding down leg. Babar flicks but manages to get just a tickle away from Carey. Single taken!
Full again, around middle this time. Sajid Khan pushes it back to the bowler.
Bye! Swinging back in, yorker-length delivery. Sajid walks across and tries to flick this but he misses. Carey dives to his left but he fails to grab the ball. The batters sneak in a bye!
Fuller now, around the fourth stum line. Babar Azam leans and pushed it back to the bowler.
Much shorter now, outside off. Babar Azam stays in his crease, hops defends it out.
Another shorter ball, around off. Babar Azam blocks it out.
NO BALL AND FOUR! Easy pickings for Sajid Khan. On a length, down the leg side. Sajid Khan flicks it towards fine leg for a boundary. Mitchell Starc has overstepped here and a no ball is given!
Full again, tailing down leg. Sajid Khan leaves it alone this time.
Tad shorter now, outside off. Sajid Khan lets that go through!
Shaping away, outside off, on a length. Sajid Khan does not fiddle with it.
Back of a length, tailing it in onto the hips. Sajid Khan tucks it towards square leg for a singe.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Babar Azam defends it out away from his body.
Much fuller now, swinging away, outside off. Babar Azam drives it past the bowler, towards long off for a single.
Marnus Labuschagne bowls medium pace instead of leg spin! Serves a length balll, outside off. Babar Azam leaves it alone!
Another length ball, around middle, at around 118 clicks. Babar Azam defends it out.
Outside off, on a length. Babar Azam offers not shot!
FOUR! Top shot! Another length ball, tailing back in, outside off, at 122 clicks. Babar Azam waits for it and punches it past cover off the back foot for a boundary.
Good-length delivery, once again coming in, around middle. Babar Azam blocks it out solidly.
Swinging in again, fuller ball, around middle. Babar Azam works it away towards Pat Cummins at mid on who slides to his right and makes a good stop! 4 runs off Marnus Labuschagne's first over!
On a length, angling down leg, at around 141 clicks. Sajid Khan leaves it alone.

OUT! CAUGHT BEHIND! Terrific bowling by Mitchell Starc, and this is an exceptional review by Australia, thanks to Alex Carey. Mitchell Starc has his third wicket, and Pakistan have lost their 7th wicket now. Beautiful ball by Mitchell Starc! This one lands on a length, shapes away a tad, outside off. Sajid Khan stays in his crease and looks to defend this, but he manages to get a slight edge towards the keeper. Alex Carey was the only one who heard a noise and convinced Pat Cummins to go for the review! The replay rolls in and UltraEdge shows there is bat involved!  The Aussies lift Carey as they see the spike on the big screen. Sajid Khan nods his head as he walks back!
Howout: c Alex Carey b Mitchell Starc

Commentary: Length ball, shapes away, down the leg side. Hasan Ali leaves it alone, Alex Carey does well to collect the ball.
Another length ball, around off. Hasan Ali defends it out.
Much fuller now, outside off. Hasan Ali leaves it alone.
Well bowled! Back of a length, outside off, shaping away. Hasan Ali stands tall and looks to defend but gets beaten!
Mitchell Swepson serves a quicker one, full, on middle. Babar Azam defends it out towards mid-wicket.
Quicker through the air again, full, around off. Babar Azam leans and defends it out.
Fuller ball, on the pads this time. Babar Azam blocks it out.
Tosses it up this time, full, outside off. Babar Azam lunges and defends this one.
Very full again, on middle. Babar Azam flicks it past mid-wicket for a single. 100 up for Pakistan!
Loopy ball, spinning it away, outside off. Hasan Ali lunges and defends it out. THAT WILL BE TEA ON DAY 3!
Mitchell Starc begins with a shorter ball, nipping back in, around middle. Babar Azam hops and defends it out.
Much fuller now, around middle. Babar Azam blocks it out solidly.
Pitches it up once again, outside off. Babar Azam drives it towards the fielder at cover.
On a length now, outside off. Babar Azam hangs back and defends it out.
Shaping away, outside off, on a length. Babar Azam lets that go through.
Good-length delivery, tailing back in, around middle, at around 141 clicks. Babar Azam blocks it out.
Length ball, sliding down the leg side. Hasan Ali misses his flick. Alex Carey dives to his left and collects the ball.
Fuller in length, nicely bowled on off. Hasan Ali digs it out.
Length ball down leg, Hasan Ali misses his tuck. The ball goes off his pads to fine leg and the batters take a leg bye.
Good-length ball, swinging it in, on off. Babar Azam drags it off the inner half to mid on.
Short ball, on off. Babar Azam pulls it straight to Mitchell Swepson at mid-wicket.
Fuller, on middle. Babar Azam flicks it to mid-wicket and takes a quick single this time to retain the strike.
Fuller in length, outside off. Babar Azam presses forward and keeps it out.
Great grab by Carey! Starc sprays it wayward, way down leg. Alex Carey dives full-stretch to his left to collect the ball.
Length ball, coming in with the angle, on middle. Babar Azam blocks it off the front foot.

OUT! RUN OUT! Another run out and Hasan Ali can continue walking back. Length ball, on middle. Babar Azam prods and taps it to covers. A little bit of confusion from the batters whether to take the single or not. Babar Azam runs a few steps and sees Hasan Ali was ready for the single so he takes off. Marnus Labuschagne at covers has ample time to score a direct hit. Very quick pickup from him and he hits the bullseye at the keeper's end. No third umpire is needed for this one and Australia again start a session with an early wicket.
Howout: run out (Marnus Labuschagne)

Commentary: Perfect delivery first up to Nauman Ali! An inswinging ball, on middle, right into the blockhole. Nauman Ali jams it out.
Full again, on middle. Ali blocks it out.
Length ball, on middle, keeps low. Babar Azam does well to nudge it on the leg side for a single.
Length ball, on the pads. Ali gets off the mark by flicking it to deep square leg for a run.
Length ball, on off, coming back in. Babar Azam jabs it to mid-wicket.
On middle, pushed to wide of mid on for a single.
Back of a length, on leg. Nauman Ali stands tall to block it on the leg side.
On a length, around off. Ali with a good block.
Fuller in length, outside off. Babar Azam drives it straight to Marnus Labuschagne at covers for a quick single. He again has a shy at the striker's end but misses. Nauman Ali was well in though.
Length ball, tailing back in, on middle. Nauman Ali looks to defend but misses. Mitchell Starc with a huge appeal but the umpire says no. Might be an inside edge there.
FOUR! Full and down leg, Nauman Ali helps it on it's way. Tickles it nicely to fine leg for a boundary.
Length, on off. Ali stays solid in his defence.
Good-length ball, outside off. Nauman Ali tries to defend but gets beaten on the outside edge.
Goes for the yorker but sprays a full toss, on middle. Ali clips it to mid on.
Touch fuller, on middle and leg. Babar Azam looks to work it on the leg side. Gets a leading egge through covers for a single.
Good length, on middle. Nauman Ali works it to deep square leg for a run.
Full and on off, Azam bunts it down to mid on for a quick single.
Full and outside off, with a bit of late movement away to whistle past Nauman's outside edge as he pushed at it.
FOUR! Finds the edge but goes through! Full and outside off, Nauman Ali looks to push. The ball goes off the outside edge through the slip cordon for a boundary.
Short of a length, outside off. Nauman Ali taps it to deep point but Babar Azam refuses to take the single. He wants to keep the strike for the next over.
Short of a length, on off. Babar Azam hops and dabs it to deep point. He does take a single this time.
Another mix up but no harm done! Full and outside off, Nauman Ali steers it to backward point. He calls for a single but is sent back by Azam. The fielder has a shy at the striker's end but misses.
Touch fuller, on middle and leg. Nauman Ali knocks it to mid on.
Short of a length, outside off. Nauman Ali has a poke at it at first but then lets it sail through.
Back of a length, on middle. Nauman Ali gets behind it to block.
Full and outside off, Nauman Ali defends it to the off side.

OUT! TAKEN! Mitchell Swepson bags his maiden Test wicket and it is of Babar Azam. He will remember this for a long time. Great captaincy from Pat Cummins. He brings Mitchell Swepson back into the attack and he doesn't disappoint. Babar Azam runs out of patience and comes charging down the track to his flighted delivery, on off. He looks to go over long off but miscues it and the ball goes up high in the air. Usman Khawaja settles himself under it nicely and snaffles it up. Babar Azam played a lone battle and has to walk back as well.
Howout: c Usman Khawaja b Mitchell Swepson

Commentary: A fuller ball, turning it in, outside off. Shaheen Afridi leans defends it out towards cover.
Tosses this one up, outside off, fuller ball. Shaheen Afridi blocks it towards mid off.
Tad shorter now, around middle. Shaheen Afridi pushes it towards mid off once again.

Bye! What beautiful delivery by Mitchell Swepson! A fuller, spinning in sharply, around middle and leg. Shaheen Afridi lunges to block this but he gets beaten as the comes spins in and beats him on the inside edge, The ball flies over the stumps and goes behind the keeper. The batters steal in a bye!
Tad shorter now, around middle. Nauman Ali stays in his crease and defends it out solidly.
Fullish ball, outside off. Shaheen Afridi lunges and defends it out solidly.
On a length, angling down leg. Shaheen Afridi misses his flick. Alex Carey dives to his right and collects the ball.

SIX! BANG! Pat Cummins drops it short now, around middle and leg. Shaheen Afridi picks up the length, and pulls it over deep square leg for a biggie! Something to cheer about for the crowd in Karachi!
Tad shorter again, outside off. Shaheen Afridi stays back and defends it out.
FOUR! Nicely done! Tad fuller now, outside off. Shaheen Afridi leans, opens the face of the bat, and guides it towards third man for a boundary!
Fuller ball, sliding down leg. Shaheen Afridi misses his flick and Alex Carey once again does well to collect the ball.
Fuller ball, spinning in, outside off. Nauman Ali drives it past cover for a single.
Half an appeal for LBW, but the umpire is unmoved! Tosses it up, full, around middle. Shaheen Afridi gets low and looks to reverse-sweep this but he misses.
Very full again, outside off. Shaheen Afridi presses forward and pushes it towards mid off.
FOUR! Good execution! Shaheen Afridi is having some fun out there in the middle! Loopy ball, full, and wide of off. Shaheen Afridi gets low and reverse-sweeps this past first slip for a boundary.
Loopy ball, full and around off. Shaheen Afridi blocks it out off the front foot.
Fuller again, quicker now, around middle. Shaheen Afridi stays back and defends it out.
Fullish delivery, around middle. Nauman Ali leans and gets an inside edge on the pads.
Full again, tosses it up, on middle. Nauman Ali defends it out off the front foot.
Firing it on the pads, shorter ball. Nauman Ali blocks it past short leg.
Beaten this time! Loopy ball, this one lands around off and turns away. Nauman Ali leans to defend but gets beaten on the outside edge.
Quicker now, full again, on middle. Nauman Ali stays un his crease and defends it out.
Quick again, on middle. Nauman Ali blocks it out off the back foot.
A full toss now, outside off. Shaheen Afridi drives it to the fielder at mid off.
Quicker, turning it in, around middle. Shaheen Afridi stays in his crease and defends it towards short leg.
Fuller ball, outside off. Shaheen Afridi pushes it with the inner half of his bat back to the bowler.
Full again, outside off. Shaheen Afridi sweeps but the ball hits the fielder at short leg.
FOUR! Up and over! Full again, tad slower, around off. Shaheen Afridi shimmies down the pitch and tonks it over mid off for a boundary.
Loopy ball, around middle. Shaheen Afridi leans and pushes it towards mid-wicket.
A stifled appeal for LBW, but turned down! Quicker now, coming in with the arm, on the pads. Nauman Ali misses his flick and gets hit on the pads. That was probably sliding down leg.
Fuller now, around middle. Nauman Ali leans and defends it out.
FOUR! Beautiful shot! Full once again, quicker now, on middle. Nauman Ali gets down on his knee and sweeps it past mid-wicket for a boundary.
Full, loopy ball, around off. Nauman Ali presses forward and defends it out.
Pitches it up once again, around middle. Nauman Ali blocks it out off the front foot.
Full, loopy ball, around middle. Nauman Ali defends it out.
Slower through the air, full, outside off. Shaheen Afridi lunges and pushes it towards cover for a single.

FOUR! EDGED AND DROPPED! A tough chance though! A fuller ball, outside off. Nauman Ali leans to block this, but the ball goes off the outside edge and lobs towards Steven Smith at first slip. He gets his left hand down to grab the ball, but manages to just get his fingers on it, and the ball races away to the fence for a boundary!
Full again, outside off. Nauman Ali presses forward and drives it but finds the fielder at cover.
Fuller ball, around middle. Shaheen Afridi defends it off the back foot.
A googly now! Fuller ball, outside off, spins away. Shaheen Afridi leans to block this but he gets beaten!

OUT! LBW! That's it! Mitchell Swepson grabs his second wicket on debut and wraps things off! A loopy ball, much slower through the air, spins in just a tad. Shaheen Afridi gets down on his knee and looks to sweep this but he misses it completely and gets rapped on his front pad. A huge appeal for LBW, and the umpire raises his finger! Shaheen Afridi opts for a review immediately! The replay rolls in. No bat involved confirms UltraEdge. Ball Tracker shows it is the umpire's call on wickets hitting. Pakistan have been bundled out for 148 and Australia have a lead of 408 runs!
Howout: lbw b Mitchell Swepson

Commentary: Shaheen Afridi starts with a length ball, well outside off. Usman Khawaja is not troubled by that and decides to let it go.
Usman Khawaja gets off the mark! Fuller in length, on off. Usman Khawaja squeezes it on the on side off the inner half for a single.
Length ball, on off, tailing away. David Warner blocks it out off the bottom of the bat.
On a good length, outside off, nipping away. Warner shoulders arms to that one.
Full and swinging away from the left-hander, Warner doesn't offer any shot.
Back of a length, on off. Warner hops and taps it to the off side. 'Noooo' shouts David Warner as there wasn't any run there.
Fuller in length, on off. Usman Khawaja steers it to deep point and crosses ends.
Fuller, on middle and leg. David Warner works it to mid-wicket and gets off the mark as well with a run.
Touch fuller, outside off. Usman Khawaja pushes it towards covers off the front foot.
On a length, outside off. Usman Khawaja knocks it in front of cover.
Confident-looking strike! Length ball, outside off. Usman Khawaja drives it through covers for a couple of runs.
Length ball, outside off. Usman Khawaja guides it to deep point for a single.
Full and on leg, Usman Khawaja flicks it to wide of mid on. The fielder there does well to stop the ball diving to his left. Keeps it down to a single.
Full and on the pads, Warner flicks it to deep square leg. Calls for two but settles for a single.
FOUR! Squeezed away! Fuller in length, outside off. Usman Khawaja leans and opens the face of the bat really late. He steers it towards the deep backward point region for a boundary.
Length ball, on off. Usman Khawaja pushes it to point for a single.
Warnes taps this length ball towards covers for a quick single.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Usman Khawaja defends it out from the crease.
On a length, around middle. David Warner taps it towards mid-wicket for a single.
Fuller this time, around middle. Usman Khawaja leans pushes it towards the fielder at mid-wicket.
Outside off now, on a length. Usman Khawaja hangs back and defends it out.
On a length, angling in on the pads. Usman Khawaja flicks it towards fine leg for a single.
DROPPED! Fuller ball, angling down leg. David Warner looks to glance but gets a slight edge back to the keeper.  Mohammad Rizwan dives to his right and fails to grab it. Tough chance though!
Fuller ball, outside off. David Warner leans and blocks it out.
Back of a length, on off. Usman Khawaja gets forward and keeps it out to the off side.
Full, on middle. Usman Khawaja flicks it to mid-wicket for a single.
Full and tailing back in, on off. David Warner blocks it out.
Bangs a well-directed bouncer, on off. David Warner does well to sway away from the line.
Touch fuller, on off. Warner pushes it towards covers.
Full again, on off. This time Warner drives it through cover-point for a run.
On a length, angling in on the pads. David Warner flicks it towards deep square leg for a brace.

OUT! CAUGHT! Pakistan have their first breakthrough! Hasan Ali strikes and gets rid of David Warner! This one was on a length, outside off. David Warner hangs back, opens the face of the bat tries to slice it in the gap between slips and gully. That was not off the edge, but unfortunately, he picks up Fawad Alam at gully, who takes a sharp catch.
Howout: c Fawad Alam b Hasan Ali

Commentary: Tad shorter, outside off, on a length. Marnus Labuschagne leaves it alone.
On the stumps, on a good length. Marnus Labuschagne tucks it towards mid-wicket.
Much fuller now, angling in, around middle. Marnus Labuschagne closes the face of his bat and pushes it towards mid-wicket.
FOUR! Marnus Labuschagne gets the off the mark in style! Length ball, angling in, on the pads. Marnus Labuschagne uses his wrists and flicks it past square leg for a boundary.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Usman Khawaja drives and finds the fielder at mid off.
On a length, down the leg side. Usman Khawaja glances it towards fine leg for a single.
Shaheen Afridi goes 'round the wicket now, serves a length ball, outside off. Marnus Labuschagne leaves it alone.
Back of a length, outside off. Marnus Labuschagne hops and taps it towards point.

Fuller now, outside off. Marnus Labuschagne presents the full face of the bat and pushes it back to the bowler. Shaheen Afridi collects the ball and mimics a throw and then stops and stares at Marnus Labuschagne. Shaheen Afridi is at it once again!
Very full again, outside off. Marnus Labuschagne leans and drives it towards deep cover for a brace.

Edged..but that does not carry! Fuller ball, outside off. Usman Khawaja leans to drive, but the ball goes off the bottom edge towards the keeper. Mohammad Rizwan tries to grab the ball on the bounce, but he fails to pouch it and the ball rolls towards third man and the batters take a single.
On a length, outside off. Marnus Labuschagne stays in his crease and defends it out.
Fraction shorter now, outside off. Marnus Labuschagne defends it towards point off the back foot.
Much fuller now, outside off. Marnus Labuschagne pushes it back to the bowler.
On a length, outside off. Marnus Labuschagne leaves it alone.
Angling in around middle, on a good length. Marnus Labuschagne tucks it towards mid-wicket.
Tosses it up, spinning away, outside off. Usman Khawaja look to drive but misses.
Very full, on leg. Usman Khawaja glances it to fine leg for a couple of runs.
FOUR! Lovely shot! Floats it up, outside off. Usman Khawaja brings out the reverse sweep. He hits it well and in the gap to deep point for a boundary.
This is pushed to sweeper cover now for a single.
Loopy ball, on middle. Marnus Labuschagne tucks it on the leg side off the back foot for a single.
Full and sliding down leg, Usman Khawaja gets low and looks to sweep hard but misses. The ball goes off the pads and rolls to fine leg. The batters take a couple of runs.
Faheem Ashraf begins with a length delivery, outside off. Marnus Labuschagne stays in his crease and pushes it towards cover.
Back of a length, outside off. Marnus Labuschagne defends it off the back foot.
